(1, 212, 'Tue Mar 24 03:10:10 +1100 2015', 'Tue Mar 24 03:10:10 +1100 2015', 'slope-flat-pricing-table', 'Slope - Flat Pricing Table', '<h2 id="item-description__slope-amp-dash-elegant-responsive-flat-pricing-table">Slope &amp;dash; Elegant Responsive Flat Pricing Table</h2>\n<strong>Slope</strong> is an elegant responsive CSS3 for your website or landing page.\n\nThe pricing table is coming in <strong>3 layouts</strong> &acirc;&#128;&#148; 3 plans, 4 plans, 3 plans + features column.\nEach layout is present in <strong>28 common flat colors</strong>. Changing the color is also very easy and described in the documentation.\nAll layouts are <strong>optimized for smartphones and tablets</strong>\n<strong>Detailed documentation</strong> will guide you through the installation and customization process. You are also welcome get your hands dirty and edit the code &amp;dash; <strong>HTML and CSS files are well commented</strong>. If you have any questions about the pricing table or just want to say &ldquo;Hi&rdquo; &amp;dash; just <a href="http://themeforest.net/user/MondayFlight#contact">send me a message</a>.\n\n	<img src="http://i.imgur.com/G9vmfDb.jpg" alt="Slope Pricing Table Features"><h2 id="item-description__this-pricing-table-features">This pricing table features:</h2>\n\n\n<li><strong>3 layouts:</strong>3 columns, 4 columns or 3 columns with a feature description column</li>\n        <li><strong>28 colors for each layout</strong></li>\n        <li><strong>Responsive</strong>, looks good on smartphones and tablets</li>\n        <li><strong>Well commented HTML and CSS</strong></li>\n        <li><strong>Detailed documentation</strong></li>\n        <li>HTML5 &amp; CSS3</li>\n        <li>Features Font Awesome icons</li>\n        <li>Support Chrome, Safari, Firefox, Opera and IE9+</li>\n        <li>CSS3 animations</li>\n        <li>Pure CSS3, no images or javascript required</li>\n        <li>Using Google Web Fonts</li>\n        <li>Valid HTML &amp; CSS</li>\n    <h2 