(30, 212, 'Fri Nov 14 04:11:17 +1100 2014', 'Fri Nov 14 04:11:17 +1100 2014', 'svg-logo-scroll-animation-css3-and-javascript', 'SVG Logo Scroll Animation | CSS3 and Javascript ', '<h2 id="item-description__svg-logo-scroll-animation-css3-and-javascript">SVG Logo Scroll Animation | CSS3 and Javascript </h2>\nScroll page to animate\nThis plug-in is a quick and easy way to add super small (&lt;4k) SVG animations to your website.  \n\nAdd interest and captivate your audience by revealing your logo, product or anything else to your website by dropping in an SVG generated file using Adobe Illustrator or <a href="https://inkscape.org/en/" rel="nofollow">Inkscape</a>.\n<h2 id="item-description__">\n<img src="http://highabovedesign.com/scrollAnimate/posting/preview3.jpg"></h2>\n<h2 id="item-description__">\n<img src="http://highabovedesign.com/scrollAnimate/posting/preview1.jpg"></h2>\n<h2 id="item-description__">\n<img src="http://highabovedesign.com/scrollAnimate/posting/preview2.jpg"></h2>\nThis plugin is split into sections so all you need to do is add some content to the &ldquo;Main&rdquo; section and then add as many sections after the animations as you like.  This plug-in also comes with a Contact Us form.', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/9383998-svg-logo-scroll-animation-css3-and-javascript-', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/111665965/MainImage.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/svg-logo-scroll-animation-css3-and-javascript-/9383998', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/svg-logo-scroll-animation-css3-and-javascript-/full_screen_preview/9383998', 7, 'animate, code, css3, javascript, logo, svg', 0, 0, 0);
