(31, 213, 'Mon Mar 23 22:40:17 +1100 2015', 'Mon Mar 23 22:40:17 +1100 2015', 'reservier', 'Reservier', '<strong>What is Reservier?</strong>\nThis is a Table Reservations App powered by Javascript, Backbone.js and PHP.<br>All informations will save as xml and json under server so no need for DB installation.<br>\nApplication includes three panels as: <a href="http://nhstudio.de/download/JS/Reservier/#admindesign" rel="nofollow">AdminDesignPanel</a>, <a href="http://nhstudio.de/download/JS/Reservier/#admincontrol" rel="nofollow">AdminControlPanel</a> and <a href="http://nhstudio.de/download/JS/Reservier" rel="nofollow">ReservationPanel</a>.\n<strong>Reservier Highlights:</strong>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Visual Panel of your Resturant Top View showing Tables positions<br> \n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Dynamic opening Times for Table Reservation [From 12:00 until 21:00]<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Ability to Block Holidays on Calender<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Multiple Reservation for one Table per Day<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Responsive user Panel for selecting Tables and do Reservation process<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Visual AdminDesignPanel for Designing your Resturant with Decorative Objects and Tables<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; AdminControlPanel for managing Reservations List<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Email Notification system for Admin and User<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Guest Reminder-email 30 Minutes before Reservation Time<br><a href="http://nhstudio.de/download/JS/Reservier/Help/help.pdf" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.nhstudio.de/images/pdf.jpg">General Help Instruction</a><br><br>\n\n\n	<strong>Requirements</strong><br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; PHP5 Server 5.0<br> \n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Browser JavaScript Enabled<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; PHP mail Server<br> \n&acirc;&#128;&cent; reservations folder should have write permission under your server<br><br>\n\n\n	<strong>Browsers Compatibility</strong><br> \n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Firefox<br> \n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Chrome<br> \n&acirc;