(35, 213, 'Fri Mar 20 13:18:03 +1100 2015', 'Fri Mar 20 13:18:03 +1100 2015', 'all-in-one-simple-ajax-php-forms', 'All in One - Simple & AJAX PHP Forms', '<img src="http://www.myflashlab.com/showcase/envato_imgs/rate-and-share-us.png"><br><a href="http://www.facebook.com/myflashlab" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.myflashlab.com/showcase/envato_imgs/follow_facebook.png"></a>\n<a href="http://codecanyon.net/user/tahadaf/follow"><img src="http://www.myflashlab.com/showcase/envato_imgs/follow_envato.png"></a>\n<a href="http://twitter.com/myflashlab" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.myflashlab.com/showcase/envato_imgs/follow_twitter.png"></a>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__our-live-prview-is-just-a-simple-demo-and-is-not-a-real-working-form-template">Our Live Prview is just a simple demo and is not a real working form template.</h3>\nAnd also <strong>please note</strong> that our Form Builder API doesn&rsquo;t create a Database to save data in it! All of the forms will just get safe data that user has entered and emails it to the recipients. That&rsquo;s actually the main job that it does!<br>\nAny other available configurations are for the sake of this process and customizing it according to your needs and ease.<br>\nSo some of our form templates like &lsquo;Donation&rsquo; and &lsquo;Registration&rsquo; forms need customized PHP codes of course. And need you to know PHP and our Advanced Usage, so that you can customize their behaviour according to your own needs.\n<br><br><h3 id="item-description__now-let-s-see-what-is-mind-blowing-about-the-form-builder">Now let&rsquo;s see what is mind blowing about the Form Builder</h3>\n<strong>\nLooking for a simple contact form for your website?<br>\nNeed a Job Application form?<br>\nFeedback form?<br>\nOr what?<br><br></strong>\n\n	Every form that you&rsquo;re looking for is available with our <strong>powerful Form Builder API</strong> and <strong>All in One package</strong>!<br><br>\n\n\n	You can easily choose from the variaty of sample avaliable forms in the package or create your own custom form! <strong>NO PHP PROGRAMMING KNOWLEDGE IS REQUIRED</strong>!<br><br>\n\n\nYou can have your own working form in two simple ways:<br><ol><li>Choose from the variety of sample avaliable forms inside of the package.</li>\n<li>Or create your own custom forms by doing it all in HTML &lsquo;form&rsquo; tag and everything else is done by our Form Builder API itself, easy!</li>\n</ol><h3 id="item-description__main-features">Main Features</h3>\n<li>No PHP programming is required (for easy usage)</li>\n<li>Powerful API Form Builder</li>\n<li><strong>Independent HTML</strong> Design</li>\n<li><strong>2 version</strong> forms, simple &amp; AJAX</li>\n<li>Secure from CSRF attacks</li>\n<li>Secure from XSS attacks</li>\n<li>Customize recipients email addresses</li>\n<li>Customize email subject</li>\n<li>Customize sender email address</li>\n<li>set an email template</li>\n<li>Set required fields</li>\n<li>File attachments support</li>\n<li>Customize file types to be uploaded</li>\n<li>Set max file size for uploads</li>\n<li>Customize error messages</li>\n<li>Customize success messages</li>\n<br><br><h3 id="item-description__sample-available-forms-all-in-both-simple-amp-ajax-versions">Sample Available Forms (All in both simple &amp; AJAX versions)</h3>\n<li>Donation form</li>\n<li>Feedback form</li>\n<li>Job Application form</li>\n<li>Login form</li>\n<li>Order form</li>\n<li>Registration form</li>\n<li>Simple Contact form</li>\n<li>Ticket Submission form</li>\n<li>And more&hellip; <strong>You can create your own form all in HTML and no PHP coding is required, Our API will take care of it!</strong></li>\n<br><br><h3 id="item-description__more-advanced-usage">More Advanced Usage?</h3>\nThen you or your programmer needs to know PHP programming too <img src="/images/smileys/happy.png" alt=":)" title=":)"><br>\nFor example when you&rsquo;re using the &lsquo;Donation&rsquo; or &lsquo;Registration&rsquo; forms