(41, 213, 'Wed Mar 18 15:10:02 +1100 2015', 'Wed Mar 25 16:58:14 +1100 2015', 'pandao-cms-pro', 'Pandao CMS pro', '\n<strong>\nDon&rsquo;t forget to rate this item after purshasing.\n</strong>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__demo-of-the-admin-panel-no-action-possible">Demo of the admin panel (no action possible)</h3>\n<a href="http://cms.pandao.eu/admin/" rel="nofollow">http://cms.pandao.eu/admin/</a> (pandao/ 123456)\n<h3 id="item-description__demo-of-the-front-office">Demo of the front office</h3>\n<a href="http://cms.pandao.eu/" rel="nofollow">http://cms.pandao.eu/</a>\n<h3 id="item-description__documentation">Documentation</h3>\n<a href="http://cms.pandao.eu/doc/" rel="nofollow">http://cms.pandao.eu/doc/</a>\n<h3 id="item-description__pandao-cms-a-web-software-to-create-and-manage-easily-your-own-website">Pandao CMS<br>\na web software to create and manage easily your own website</h3>\nPandao CMS is a professional and complete <strong>Content Managment System</strong> which contains an ergonomic admin panel which allows you to manage easily the content of your website coupled with an easyly customizable template.<br><strong>Ideal for a Web agency wishing to spread web sites quickly and simply for its customers!</strong><br>\nPandao CMS is <strong>fully responsive</strong>, so use it as well on your smartphone as on your computer.\nBased on PDO/MySQL &ndash; PHP4/5 &ndash; HTML5 &ndash; CSS3 &ndash; Bootstrap 3.x\n<img src="http://cms.pandao.eu/doc/assets/images/steps.png" alt="Steps"><h3 id="item-description__included-template">Included Template</h3>\n<img src="http://cms.pandao.eu/doc/assets/images/template.jpg" alt="Features"><h3 id="item-description__features">Features</h3>\n<li>Quick install in <strong>5 minutes only!</strong> (quick installation wizard, no skill required)</li>\n<li>Portable: localhost, root, subdirectory, subdomain or not&hellip; Wherever you like!</li>\n<li>Easy to customize (manage your own templates and models)</li>\n<li>User friendly</li>\n<li>Inuitive admin panel</li>\n<li><strong>Create easily pages</strong>, subpages, articles and choose your layout</li>\n<li>Powerful Ajax file manager (videos, images, documents)</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable comments on the articles</li>\n<li>Create and customize widgets</li>\n<li>Powerfull search engine</li>\n<li><strong>Fully responsive design</strong> (front office and back office)</li>\n<li>Multi-language (add new languages and manage your translations)</li>\n<li>SEO ready (clean URL, structured datas, respect for the principles of Google&hellip;)</li>\n<li>High performance level (page speed optimization)</li>\n<li>Powerfull security (CSRF, XSS, SQL Injection)</li>\n<li>Customizable and scalable back office</li>\n<li>Light weight</li>\n<li>Icons font (Font Awesome)</li>\n<li>Google Maps API V3</li>\n<li>Helpful documentation</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__admin-modules">Admin Modules</h3>\n<li>Pages</li>\n<li>Articles</li>\n<li>Comments</li>\n<li>Gallery</li>\n<li>Languages</li>\n<li>Medias</li>\n<li>Slideshow</li>\n<li>Tags</li>\n<li>Texts</li>\n<li>Widgets</li>\n<li>Create your own modules (ex: rooms, products, employees&hellip;)</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__technologies-and-js-plugins">Technologies and JS Plugins</h3>\n<li>PHP 4.x / PHP 5.x</li>\n<li>MySQL 5.x</li>\n<li>HTML 5</li>\n<li>CSS 3</li>\n<li>Javascript</li>\n<li>jQuery</li>\n<li>Bootstrap 3.x</li>\n<li>Ajax</li>\n<li>Font Awesome</li>\n<li>CKEditor</li>\n<li>Royal Slider (You save 14$)</li>\n<li>Isotope</li>\n<li>Owl Carousel</li>\n<li>Modernizr</li>\n<li>Uploadifive</li>\n<li>Magnific Popup</li>\n<li>ToolMan</li>\n<li>TableDnd</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__updates">Updates</h3>\n<h4 id="item-description__update-march-18-2015">Update March 18, 2015</h4>\n<strong>Fixed issues:</strong><br>- Bug on adding comments fixed in article.php\n<h4 id="item-description__update-march-20-2015">Update March 20, 2015</h4>\n<strong>New feature / Improvements:</strong><br>- Translate the back office via the file /admin/includes/lang.ini\n<h4 id="item-description__update-march-24-2015">Update March 24, 2015</h4>\n<strong>Fixed issues:</strong><br>- Articles links in sitemap.php<br>- Click on main menu on mobile devices\n<h4 id="item-description__update-march-25-2015">Update March 25, 2015</h4>\n<strong>New feature / Improvements:</strong><br>- Adding date, tags and number of comments displayed into the articles in page.php<br>- Media manager in the admin panel\n<strong>Fixed issues:</strong><br>- Invalid recipient variables in contact.php<br>- Documentation: wrong variable value for .htaccess', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10768918-pandao-cms-pro', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126934193/preview2.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/pandao-cms-pro/10768918', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/pandao-cms-pro/full_screen_preview/10768918', 32, 'admin, administration, back end, back office, bootstrap, cms, content management system, interface, manager, panel, responsive, site, template', 0, 0, 0),
(42, 213, 'Thu Mar 19 16:51:44 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 19 16:51:44 +1100 2015', 'up-instant-photo-sharing', 'UP - Instant Photo Sharing', '<h2 id="item-description__demo">Demo:</h2>\n<a href="http://up-sharing.com" rel="nofollow">http://up-sharing.com</a><br><a href="http://up-sharing.com/cp" rel="nofollow">http://up-sharing.com/cp</a> (Administration &ndash; username: <strong>admin</strong>, password: <strong>admin</strong>)\n<br><br>\nUP it&rsquo;s an instant photo sharing platform. Anyone can create their own album (no registration or apps required) in seconds. Manage album photos or upload more, set album title or privacy (public/private), share the album with your friends. Browse public albums, sort them by popularity or name.<br><br><img src="http://up-sharing.com/screens/screen_1.jpg"><h2 id="item-description__responsive-for-your-mobile">Responsive for your mobile</h2>\n<img src="http://up-sharing.com/screens/screen_2.jpg"><h2 id="item-description__or-tablet">Or tablet</h2>\n<img src="http://up-sharing.com/screens/screen_3.jpg"><br><h2 id="item-description__features">Features</h2>\nOne click install<br>\nHomepage backgrounds (5 included)<br>\nOption to set the upload box to the left or right side<br>\nFriendly URL&rsquo;s<br>\nMultiple photos upload<br>\nAlbum privacy public/private<br>\nOption to remove album<br>\nCopy album link or admin link from album option<br>\nShare album on facebook/twitter<br>\nInfinite onscroll pagination on browse albums and album page<br>\nOption to download photo (original size)<br>\nBrowse public albums page<br>\nOption to sort public albums by Date, Views, Photos count, Album name<br>\nAlbum photos management (remove multiple photos in same time)<br>\nLanguage system (english,romanian,francais, deutsch included)<br>\nRetina ready for iPhone/iPad<br>\nJPG,PNG,GIF photos supported<br>\nMobile optimized (support almost any smartphone)<br>\nTablet optimized (support almost any tablet)<br>\nNo refresh (browse anything from the site without refreshing)<br>\nMetro style (for album photos)<br>\nFaq page (editable from Administration panel)<br>\nTerms page (editable from Administration panel)<br>\nFooter coypright (editable from Administration panel)<br>\nCustom header bar (editable from Administration panel)<br>\nCustom meta tags (editable from Administration panel)<br>\nFullscreen photo bar position top/bottom (editable from Administration panel)<br>\nAdministration panel (stats,manage albums, manage photos, manage site settings)<br>\nClean code, well organised script assets<br>\nDocumentation<br><h2 id="item-description__extra">Extra</h2>\nTop support (from 5 stars author)<br>\nFree updates lifetime<br><h2 id="item-description__requirements">Requirements</h2>\nAny webhosting with PHP 5.3+<br>\nRewriteModule enabled<br>\nGD Image (any webhosting has it)<br>\nMySQL with MySQLi extension (any webhosting has it)', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10796684-up-instant-photo-sharing', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126433518/envato_preview.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/up-instant-photo-sharing/10796684', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/up-instant-photo-sharing/full_screen_preview/10796684', 25, 'album, browse albums, create album, flikr, photo gallery, photo sharing, up, upload', 0, 0, 0),
(43, 213, 'Wed Mar 18 15:09:20 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 26 17:49:36 +1100 2015', 'esotalk-forum-plugin-envato-licensing-validate-purchaser', 'esoTalk Forum Plugin: Envato Licensing & Validate Purchaser', '<strong>esoTalk &ndash; ENVATO plugin &ndash; Protect your forum from users without a (specified) purchased product from your envato account.</strong>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__forum-software">Forum Software</h3>\nThis is a plugin for the esoTalk Fat-free forum software. Please ensure you have installed the latest version of <a href="http://esotalk.org/" rel="nofollow">esoTalk</a> before using this plugin.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__plugin-envato-licensing-amp-validate-purchaser">Plugin: Envato Licensing &amp; Validate Purchaser</h3>\nThis plugin allows you to interact with your buyers in one way. It only allow registration for valide purchasers of an envato product, so it significantly improves your after sales support and customer satisfaction.\nThrough the use of this plugin a long with your esoTalk Forum you can provide customers access to a complete Forum for your Support.\nCustomers can register only with there purchase code to their account allowing them to post support questions. As an Admin you can then see only real  customers (item purchased) in your Forums.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__function">Function</h3>\n<li>1. Option: Only a user with valid envato product purchase code can register</li>\n    <li>2. Option: Only a purchase code owner of a special product can register</li>\n    <li>3. Option: Every purchase code can be used only one times</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__changelog">Changelog</h3>\n<pre>\n    Version 1.2 (25.03.2015)\n    + Added: Options to allow only one Registration with one Purchase Code\n    + Improved: If Plugin is activ the Purchase Code is a Required Field\n    + Fixed: Some Small Code Improvements\n\n    Version 1.1 (20.03.2015)\n    + Added: Options to allow only a special Item ID owner to Register\n\n    Version 1.0 (18.03.2015)\n    + First Release of this esoTalk Forum Add-On on CodeCanyon\n</pre>', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10736379-esotalk-forum-plugin-envato-licensing-validate-purchaser', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126574694/Inline%20Preview%20Image.png', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/esotalk-forum-plugin-envato-licensing-validate-purchaser/10736379', '', 8, 'api, envato, envato api, esotalk, esotalk forum, forum, forum plugin, license, licensing, register, registration, validate, validate user, validate users', 0, 0, 0),
(44, 213, 'Mon Mar 16 17:56:03 +1100 2015', 'Wed Mar 18 15:06:19 +1100 2015', 'author-support-desk', 'Author Support Desk', '<a href="http://nexthon.com/" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/EYVZwUZ.png"></a><a href="http://facebook.com/nexthon" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/jHX0C8k.png"></a><a href="http://twitter.com/nexthon" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/8mAr7rn.png"></a><a href="http://nexthon.ticksy.com" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/5lfX8a1.png"></a>\n\n\nAuthor Support Desk makes support simple again. You don&rsquo;t need the headache or the expense or the bloatware &ndash; and neither do your customers. Whether they reach out to you with questions, want to find answers on their own, or need to be proactively engaged, Author Support Desk makes communicating with customers easy and efficient. Your service desk isn&rsquo;t just software. It&rsquo;s where agents meet users; where people meet technology. Author Support Desk makes sure that agents are able to support users with minimum fuss, &amp; at the same time enjoy themselves, driving up efficiency &amp; productivity. Which means happier agents &amp; happier users, all thanks to a stunningly efficient Author Support Desk. Author Support Desk lets you customize your colors to match your brand for a seamless customer experience. Author Support Desk is designed to easily integrate with Envato, making it simple to import Envato products and verify purchases. Author Support Desk clean design and interface makes the support process simple and intuitive for you and &ndash; more importantly &ndash; your customers.\n\n<h2 id="item-description__admin-login-details">Admin Login Details</h2>\n<a href="http://muvaa.com/support/" rel="nofollow">http://muvaa.com/support/</a><br>\nUsername : <a href="mailto:nexthon@live.com">nexthon@live.com</a><br>\nPassword : administrator<br>\nDemo : <a href="http://muvaa.com/support/" rel="nofollow">http://muvaa.com/support/</a><br><h2 id="item-description__features">Features</h2>\n<li>Envato API Support</li>\n<li>Employees Management</li>\n<li>Envato Product Verification</li>\n<li>Email Notifications</li>\n<li>Custom Branding Support</li>\n<li>Public/Private Tickets</li>\n<li>Tickets Search</li>\n<li>Files Attachment</li>\n<li>Facebook Login</li>\n<li>SMTP Support</li>\n<li>Frequently Asked Questions</li>\n<li>Google Material Design</li>\n<li>100% Responsive Design</li>\n<li>Quick and Easy Installation</li>\n<li>Easy to Use</li>\n<li>and more&hellip;</li>\n<a href="http://eepurl.com/beKN_H" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/HWq1bwG.png"></a>\n<h2 id="item-description__requirements">Requirements</h2>\n<li>Operating System : Linux</li>\n<li>Web Server : Apache</li>\n<li>PHP Version: 5.4+</li>\n<li>PHP allow_url_fopen</li>\n<li>PHP GD Library</li>\n<li>PHP Multi byte String</li>\n<li>PHP CURL</li>\n<li>MySql: 5.0+</li>\n<h2 id="item-description__change-log">Change Log</h2>\n<br><strong>Version 1.0 [13-3-2015]</strong>\n<pre>\n- Initial Release.\n</pre>', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10760044-author-support-desk', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126052202/cover.png', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/author-support-desk/10760044', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/author-support-desk/full_screen_preview/10760044', 30, 'author support desk, easy support desk, envato support desk, material design, materialize support desk, nexthon support desk, php support desk, php support script, php support system, support desk', 0, 0, 0),
(45, 213, 'Mon Mar 16 17:45:29 +1100 2015', 'Tue Mar 17 14:44:41 +1100 2015', 'rufus-gui-for-tequila', 'Rufus GUI for Tequila', '<a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/tequila-file-hosting-script/7604312"><img src="http://themedema.altervista.org/page-rufus.png"></a>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__about-this-product">ABOUT THIS PRODUCT</h3>\nRufus is a modern and functional theme for Tequila. It is designed in Material Design.\n<br><br> Design<br> The user interface has been designed to meet the user. Every detail is taken care of.\n&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;Responsive &amp; Retina<br> Each element of Rufus is responsive and adaptable to all devices.\nFree Support<br> Customer satisfaction is our first priority, so we offer a free support service.\n&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;<br>Increased Speed<br> Tequila has been lightened and optimized to achieve maximum speed.\n<h3 id="item-description__support">SUPPORT</h3>\n Customer satisfaction is our first priority, so we offer a free support service. To get in touch with us, open a ticket in our system <a href="http://www.themedema.com/ss" rel="nofollow">http://www.themedema.com/ss</a>, we will reply as soon as possible. P.S.: If you have problems with our support system (which is in BETA), you can contact us by email at <a href="mailto:themedema@outlook.it"> themedema@outlook.it</a>.\n<h3 id="item-description__updates">UPDATES</h3>\n<pre>\nV1.0 -16/03/2015\n</pre>', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10754313-rufus-gui-for-tequila', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126489101/cover.png', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/rufus-gui-for-tequila/10754313', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/rufus-gui-for-tequila/full_screen_preview/10754313', 8, 'cloud, file, gui, hosting, material design, script, tequila', 0, 0, 0),
