(50, 213, 'Sun Mar 15 04:34:11 +1100 2015', 'Sun Mar 15 04:34:11 +1100 2015', 'seo-keyword-competition', 'SEO Keyword Competition', 'The <strong>SEO Keyword Competition</strong> is a script which gives you an easy but incredibly powerful way to assess the level of competition in any particular niche.<br>\nNo need expension tool (MS,LTP,..)...\n <br><br>\nOur SEO Keyword Competition tool provides an SERP analysis of the first page in Google, telling you how hard it would be to beat your competition. \n <br><br>\nYou see the first 10 URL&rsquo;s, plus metrics about the sites, with on-page SEO and off-page SEO; like PageRank, Alexa Rank, DMOZ, Domain Age, presence of keyword in metadata.<br>\nThe metrics are colour-coded, where green pretty means: not too well optimized, so not hard to beat\n <br><br>What is keyword competition? Keyword competition is the measure of how difficult it will be to rank for a particular keyword. The competition for a keyword can vary depending on how popular the keyword is and industry competition.\n <br><br><strong>Features</strong>\n<li>No Database is Required.</li>\n<li>Free MOZ API</li>\n<li>Alexa Rank</li>\n<li>Google Page Rank</li>\n<li>Google Indexed webpage</li>\n<li>Dmoz Check Listed</li>\n<li>Domain Age</li>\n<li>MOZ rank + backlinks</li>\n<li>if the keywords is in the URL</li>\n<li>if the keywords is in the Title</li>\n<li>if the keywords is in the Description (meta tag)</li>\n<li>if the keywords is in the headlines (h1)</li>\n<li>Word count in the webpage</li>\n<li>Keywords occurence in the webpage</li>\n<br><br><strong>Requirements</strong>\n<li>Operating System : Linux</li>\n<li>Web Server : Apache</li>\n<li>PHP Version: 5.4 or Higher</li>\n<li>PHP allow_url_fopen ON</li>\n<li>Extension php_openssl ON</li>\n', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10724002-seo-keyword-competition', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/125798948/Preview.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/seo-keyword-competition/10724002', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/s