(53, 213, 'Sat Mar 14 02:54:05 +1100 2015', 'Sat Mar 14 02:54:05 +1100 2015', 'flora-forms-responsive-ajax-contact-forms', 'Flora Forms -  Responsive Ajax Contact Forms', 'Flora Forms is a set of simple easy to use Clean HTML5 CSS3 responsive forms, with common features for a website contact or order form. It utilizes the power  of PHP and AJAX to send form data to your email address or a group of email addresses without page reload. In addition the form includes a realtime anti-span CAPTCHA for protecting you against common spam bots and spam emails, it also includes an added layer of both serverside and clientside validation , a visual file upload progressbar tracker, Six beautifully designed themes and multiple HTML5 form elements.\n\nWith Flora forms you can choose to use the normal server mail or SMTP functions to send form data. You can also easily extend the form by adding or removing form fields easily, building more complex layouts using the 12 column grid, plus optimizations for mobile devices and high resolution retina screens, as well as mobile device HTML5 input virtual keyboard detection for improved user experience.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__form-features">Form Features</h3>\n<li>Multiple HTML5 CSS3 form inputs</li>\n    <li>CSS3 File inputs or file uploaders </li>\n    <li>CSS3 checkboxes radios</li>\n    <li>CSS3 toggle switches</li>\n    <li>Tooltips + vector icons </li>\n    <li>Notification alert messages </li>\n    <li>CSS3 buttons </li>\n    <li>Animated progress bars </li>\n    <li>Responsive 12 column grid  </li>\n    <li>Ajax form processing </li>\n    <li>Form validation  </li>\n    <li>6 color themes </li>\n    <li>Responsive HTML email templates </li>\n    <li>Clientside and serverside validation</li>\n    <li>File upload progress</li>\n    <li>CSV file export </li>\n    <li>Anti Spam AJAX CAPTCHA </li>\n    <li>SMTP and Sendmail support </li>\n    <li>Accessible modern form fields</li>\n    <li>Retina ready</li>\n<strong>10.03.2015 &n