(55, 213, 'Thu Mar 12 17:56:17 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 12 17:56:17 +1100 2015', 'webrtc-videocall-twitter-edition', 'WebRTC VideoCall Twitter Edition', '<h2 id="item-description__webrtc-videocall-twitter-edition">WebRTC VideoCall Twitter edition</h2>\nPrivate One on One Video chat for Twitter users only<br>\nThis version uses the twitter api to generate a personal ID from the loged twitter users username<br>\nThere are no two twitter accounts with the same user name it&rsquo;s uniek ID and never already taken<br>\nBasicly it&rsquo;s like a phone number if you always use the same room<br><br>\nStandalone One on One private Webcam Video Chat WebRTC<br><br>\nRealtime audio and video communications Browser to Browser! P2P<br>\nThe audio and video stream goes NOT over your server so there is Almost No cpu or bandwidth usage, it runs also very  smoot on a shared hosting.<br><br> \nIt&rsquo;s a meeting place for twitter users and friends to talk face to face\nAlso Great to promote your deals<br><br>\nit&rsquo;s a very lightweight webcam application and yet very powerful\nUsers can use the chat rooms on the fly<br>\nJust give the room url and ID to a twitter user or friend to start the private video chat.<br><br> \nPrivate one-on-one video calls<br>\nNo software to install this script runs direct in your browser (Chrome OR Firefox)<br>\nNo need to install additional software or plugins No sign up!<br>\nAll that your vistiors need is a webcam and a twitter account<br><br>\nBuilt with bootstrap 3, Javascript HTML5<br>\nWebRTC = Web based Real Time Communications technology.<br>\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__features">Features</h2>\n\n	One on One Video calls<br>\n15 Video chat locations to split traffic and provide even more uniek rooms<br>\nChatrooms are extendeble<br>\nAll rooms have a select copy and share modal (url and key)<br>\nSocial Share and like buttons<br>\nEasy monetise 2 Adspots in every room and 2 on the home page<br>\nBuild on bootstrap 3 HTML5<br>\nNo Flash<br>\