(69, 214, 'Wed Mar 18 07:43:28 +1100 2015', 'Wed Mar 18 07:43:28 +1100 2015', 'uber-google-maps-for-jquery', 'UBER Google Maps for jQuery', '<img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/1.png"><img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/2.png"><img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/3.png"><img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/4.png"><img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/5.png"><img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/6.png"><img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/7.png"><a href="http://webcraft.cc/support.php" rel="nofollow">\n    <img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/8.png"></a>\n<a href="http://webcraft.cc/" rel="nofollow">\n    <img src="http://webcraft.cc/uploads/uber-google-maps/description-jquery/9.png"></a>\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__uber-google-maps-for-jquery">UBER Google Maps for jQuery</h2>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__100-built-in-styles">100+ Built-in Styles</h3>\nUber Google Maps comes with more than 100 styles to choose from. Find the colors that match your website perfectly, or create a custom style with a third-party editor.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__fullscreen-support">Fullscreen Support</h3>\nGive your users the option to enter fullscreen mode. They will thank you for it!\n\n<h3 id="item-description__localization">Localization</h3>\nUber Google Maps supports more than 50 languages. Pretty much every language that is supported by the Google Maps API.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__responsive">Responsive</h3>\nIf your site is responsive, you can&rsquo;t go wrong with Uber Google Maps. It has an option to be responsive, or &ldquo;flexible width&rdquo;.', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10808350-uber-google-maps-for-jquery', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126547251/inline.png', 'http: