(74, 214, 'Sat Mar 14 04:54:09 +1100 2015', 'Wed Mar 18 06:33:38 +1100 2015', 'mateffects-a-jquery-pack-based-on-material-design', 'MatEffects- A jQuery Pack Based On Material Design', '<img src="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/promo/top.jpg">\n\n\n	<a href="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/demo/over-view.html" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/promo/ov-btn.jpg"></a>\n<a href="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/demo/section-navigator.html" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/promo/sn-btn.jpg"></a>\n<a href="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/demo/group-slider.html" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/promo/gs-btn.jpg"></a>\n<a href="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/demo/color-slider.html" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/promo/cs-btn.jpg"></a>\n\n\n	<img src="http://www.sktajbir.com/jEffectbox/mateffects/promo/make-sure.jpg">\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__plugin-features">Plugin Features</h3>\n<li>Based on Google&rsquo;s Material design.</li>\n<li>Includes hover effect, slider, pop up/modal,  section scroller.</li>\n<li>One effect can be used multiple times in a single page.</li>\n<li>Four modern jQuery effects included in the package.</li>\n<li>Very lightweight, minified version is only 14kb.</li>\n<li>Control settings of each effects.</li>\n<li>Control appearance through CSS, so it can be restyled and match any design.</li>\n<li>Supports all major browsers.</li>\n<li>Supports desktop, laptop, tablet/mobile devices.</li>\n<li>Specially developed for Material Design Lovers.</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__download-file-includes">Download file includes:</h3>\n<ol><li>4 templates showing the use of 4 different effects which are shown in the live preview.</li>\n<li>Library, where you&rsquo;ll get jquery.mateffects-1.0.5.js, jquery.mateffects-1.0.5.min.js, mateffect