(88, 214, 'Fri Feb 27 10:24:03 +1100 2015', 'Sun Mar 01 10:21:21 +1100 2015', 'materialstart-responsive-fullscreen-panel', 'MaterialStart - Responsive Fullscreen Panel', '<a href="http://codecanyon.net/user/SOHN/follow"><img src="http://img.sonhlab.com/buttons/envato-connect.png"></a>\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sonhlab" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://img.sonhlab.com/buttons/fb-connect.png"></a>\n<a href="https://twitter.com/SONHlab" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://img.sonhlab.com/buttons/tt-connect.png"></a>\n<a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/b/102785063617764907816/" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://img.sonhlab.com/buttons/gg-connect.png"></a>\n\n\n	<strong>MaterialStart</strong> is a jQuery plugin that allows you to create fullscreen panels, lightboxes, popups in your page with a left navigation menu bar, make unlimited panels as you want and support for responsive design. You can combine Inline and AJAX content, show them automatically OR via an URL param OR clicking on a button. By these power functions, this plugin will bring you an easy way to control and display your complex content.\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features:</h3>\n<li>Unlimited Content, Unlimited NavBar</li>\n<li>Responsive Design.</li>\n<li>Support to Show Content Automatically.</li>\n<li>Open by Click and URL Param.</li>\n<li>Support to change URL and Back Event.</li>\n<li>Support Inline and AJAX content.</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__documentation">Documentation</h3>\n<a href="http://docs.sonhlab.com/materialstart-jquery-full-screen-material-design-panel/" rel="nofollow">MaterialStart Documentation</a>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__before-purchase"><strong>Before Purchase:</strong></h3>\nMy items are always provided with demos. So please check my demos and <a href="http://docs.sonhlab.com/basic-support-service/" rel="nofollow">Support Information</a> before purchasing.\n\n	If you have any questions related to my items you can go to my <a href="http://talk.sonhlab.com" 