i>The design is done by our pal John Frasko &ndash; check him out here &ndash; <a href="https://dribbble.com/john_pixle" rel="nofollow">https://dribbble.com/john_pixle</a> </li>\n', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10714484-tauno-a-blog-magazine-psd-template', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/125692199/01_main_preview.__large_preview.jpg', 'http://themeforest.net/item/tauno-a-blog-magazine-psd-template/10714484', '', 10, 'agency, blog, business, clean, corporate, creative, design, magazine, modern, news, personal, photography, portfolio, responsive, studio', 0, 0, 0),
