(129, 216, 'Mon Mar 23 06:52:16 +1100 2015', 'Sat Mar 28 01:42:31 +1100 2015', 'grid-x-creative-multipurpose-theme', 'GRID X - Creative MultiPurpose Theme', '<img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/01.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/02.gif" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/03.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/04.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/05.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/06.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/07.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/07-a.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/08.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/09.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/09-a.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/10.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"><a href="http://demo.themeton.com/gridx" rel="nofollow">\n<img src="http://themeton.com/forenvatoimg/gridx/11.png" alt="Grid X Presentation"></a>\n\n\n	<strong>Grid X</strong> is a creative multipurpose theme that fits any type of sites, including Corporate, Blog, Portfolio, Grid and Creative sites. We&rsquo;ve inserted 21+ grid pages, 7 completely different Home pages and 5 creative pages for your taste into the demo site those presents power of the template and you can mix them and build your own.\n\n\n	You can find many grid themes or plugins here, but Grid X has <strong>3 unique</strong> types of opening styles. <a href="http://template.themeton.com/gridx/grid.html?grid=x&amp;style=3&amp;open=push-state" rel="nofollow">Push open</a>, <a href="http://template.themeton.com/gridx/grid.html?grid=style&amp;style=3&amp;open=open-gi" rel="nofollow">Middle open</a> (inspired Google Image) and <a href="http://template.themeton.com/gridx/grid.html?grid=style&amp;style=3" rel="nofollow">Modal</a>. Also it comes with Visual Composer, Ultimate Addons and Revolution slider that helps you to build your beautiful modern websites as you wish.\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__key-features">Key Features</h2>\n<li>Header Layouts</li>\n    <li>Menu Styles</li>\n    <li>Responsive &amp; Retina ready</li>\n    <li>Translation ready</li>\n    <li>Included Visual Composer, Save $28</li>\n<li>Default 37 elements</li>\n    <li>Additional 6 elements</li>\n<li>Ultimate AddOns for VC, Save $17</li>\n<li>Advanced 32 elements &amp; amazing powerful options</li>\n<li>Powerful Revolution Slider, Save $18</li>\n    <li>Fullscreen &amp; Fullwidth sections</li>\n    <li>Live Customizer 100+ options</li>\n    <li>Advanced typography, 600+ Google Fonts</li>\n    <li>One click demo data</li>\n    <li>LESS based clean styling</li>\n    <li>SEO friendly</li>\n    <li>Dark / Light styling</li>\n    <li>Unlimited color</li>\n    <li>Wide &amp; Boxed Layouts, flexible width.</li>\n    <li>Up to 4 column Footer</li>\n    <li>Additional 3 widgets</li>\n    <li>Supports Google Fonts</li>\n    <li>Well documented</li>\n    <li>Free updates &amp; support</li>\n<h4 id="item-description__advanced-grid-x-element">Advanced <strong>Grid X Element</strong></h4>\nThis is what we exactly offering you more than others. This custom Visual Composer element has following bright features and you can build any custom Grid X layout with your posts, portfolio and pages.\n<li><strong>Layout group</strong> : Grid X / Even / Masonry</li>\n    <li><strong>Overlay style</strong> : 9 completely different styles</li>\n    <li><strong>Size option</strong> : You can choose column number, ratio width or width size depending on your selected layout style</li>\n    <li><strong>Opening types</strong> : Modal / Push / Inline</li>\n    <li><strong>Pagination</strong> : Infinite / Regular</li>\n    <li><strong>Category filter</strong></li>\n    <li><strong>Gutter space</strong> : Between grid posts</li>\n    <li><strong>Query filter</strong> : Selection for your post type and category/taxonomy </li>\n<h4 id="item-description__advanced-page-options">Advanced <strong>Page options</strong></h4>\n<li>Individual Header style</li>\n    <li>Menu Align</li>\n    <li>Page title styling including spacing, background color, image, text color and overlay color fill</li>\n    <li>Page top slider</li>\n    <li>Page layout: Full/Right/Left sidebar</li>\n<h4 id="item-description__advanced-portfolio-post-options">Advanced <strong>Portfolio post options</strong></h4>\n<li>Gallery slider</li>\n    <li>Video</li>\n    <li>Portfolio custom details : Structured list</li>\n    <li>Page top slider</li>\n    <li>Page layout: Full/Right/Left sidebar</li>\n', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10765043-grid-x-creative-multipurpose-theme', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127900661/gridx-screenshots/preview-image.__large_preview.png', 'http://themeforest.net/item/grid-x-creative-multipurpose-theme/10765043', 'http://themeforest.net/item/grid-x-creative-multipurpose-theme/full_screen_preview/10765043', 58, 'ajax, canvas, customizer, dark, grid, grid x, inline, left header, less, mobile first, modal, push, square, transparent, visual composer', 0, 0, 0),
