(135, 216, 'Sun Mar 22 16:32:13 +1100 2015', 'Sun Mar 22 16:32:13 +1100 2015', 'lifemag-responsive-magazine-wordpress-theme', 'LifeMag - Responsive Magazine WordPress Theme', '<a href="http://themeforest.net/user/magentech"> <img src="http://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/themeforest-box/follow-evato.jpg" alt="\\\\"></a> <a href="http://facebook.com/magentech" rel="nofollow"> <img src="http://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/themeforest-box/follow-fb.jpg" alt="\\\\"></a> <a href="http://magentech.com/submit-a-ticket/" rel="nofollow"> <img src="http://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/themeforest-box/support.jpg" alt="\\\\"></a> <a href="http://www.magentech.com/documentation/sw-lifemag/" rel="nofollow"> <img src="http://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/themeforest-box/guide.jpg" alt="\\\\"></a>\n<h2 id="item-description__lifemag-simple-yet-elegant-wordpress-theme-for-news-magazine-websites">Lifemag &ndash; Simple yet Elegant WordPress Theme for News/Magazine websites</h2>\nLifemag is a simple yet elegant, multipurpose theme. Following the new trends in design, this is an eye-catching and straightforward theme with flat design, 5 color presets, neat typography, smooth navigation and well-structured layout. Lifemag would be a perfect choice for any news, newspaper, magazine, publishing or review website&hellip;\nFurthermore, this amazing theme is integrated with many plugins with lots of features, custom widgets, unlimited color schemes, Slider Resolution with smooth transition effects, Mega Menu with multiple column styles and advanced widgets&hellip; You are free to control this theme in order to make your store more friendly and adorable for your customers..\nLet&rsquo;s experience this awesomeness and to explore more features in this theme. We are sure that you will fall in love with our Lifemag at first sight.\n <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/list-features.png" alt="Lifemag - WordPress Theme" title="Lifemag - WordPress Theme">\n\n<h3 id="item-description__unlimited-color-styles">UNLIMITED COLOR STYLES</h3>\n<img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/color.png" alt="SW Lifemag - Color Presets" title="SW Lifemag - Color Presets">\nThis theme comes with a lots of color styles: Cyan, Blue, Red, Orange and Green. Besides, it gives you the full control in customizing color schemes in back-end.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__responsive-design">RESPONSIVE DESIGN</h3>\n  <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/Responsive.png" alt="SW Lifemag - Fully Responsive" title="SW Lifemag - Fully Responsive">Lifemagis designed to be fully responsive layout, it will make your site have amazing look on different screen resolutions such as: mobile, iPhone, iPad and other tablets. This is one of the best option to reach the customers who use smart devices.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__homepage-layouts">HOMEPAGE LAYOUTS</h3>\n<img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/homepage.png" alt="SW Lifemag - Homepage" title="SW Lifemag - Homepage">\n\n<h3 id="item-description__header-styles">HEADER STYLES</h3>\n  <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/headers.png" alt="Style - Header styles" title="Style - Header styles"><h3 id="item-description__menu-styles">MENU STYLES</h3>\n  <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/menu.png" alt="Style - Menu styles" title="Style - Menu styles">You can easy to create columns to display categories and products with description, price, image, video, effects&hellip; or even add links to any page, widgets with promotion banners and plugins.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__stunning-slideshow">STUNNING SLIDESHOW</h3>\n<img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/grid_slider.gif" alt="SW Lifemag - Slideshow" title="SW Lifemag - Slideshow">\nThis theme promise that it will attract the highest viewer&rsquo;s attention when surfing your site by using Slider. Supporting tons of transition effects, an image preloader, video embedding, autoplay that stops on user interaction and lots of easy to set options to create your own effects just from the admin.\n<li>Create image slideshow widget instance and display on any position</li>\n<li>Create unlimited layered per slide, configure various effects.</li>\n<li>Configure slideshow effect, auto sliding, thumbnail, text, navigation&hellip;</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__translation-support-amp-rtl-language-ready">TRANSLATION SUPPORT &amp; RTL LANGUAGE READY</h3>\n <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/multi-language.png" alt="SW Lifemag - RTL Language Ready" title="SW Lifemag - RTL Language Ready">\nThis theme is fully compatible with the WPML multilingual plugin, you can translate your website to any language. SW Lifemagcomes in two languages versions: LTR and RTL to respond to users who communicate with a right-to-left language. Theme includes setting the direction: RTL CSS style and adjusting widget layout and behavior accordingly, and RTL will be activated when you set up RTL language in WP-Config.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__useful-shortcodes">USEFUL SHORTCODES</h3>\n <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/short-code.png" alt="SW Lifemag - Shortcodes Ready" title="SW Lifemag - Shortcodes Ready">\nTheme includes tons of useful built-in Shortcodes such as: Columns, Slideshow, Button, Google Map&hellip; You can create advanced custom content with minimal effort or even without any knowledge how to code HTML. Shortcodes can be used anywhere in pages, posts and also in menu.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__advance-admin-panel">ADVANCE ADMIN PANEL</h3>\n <img src="https://smartaddons.s3.amazonaws.com/images/PR-templates/themeforest/wordpress/sw-lifemag/admin-panel.png" alt="SW Lifemag - Admin Panel" title="SW Lifemag - Admin Panel">\n\n<h3 id="item-description__full-feature-list">Full Feature List</h3>\n<li>Compatible with WordPress 3.9.1</li>\n<li>Compatible with IE9+, Firefox 4+, Netscape, Safari, Opera 9.5 and Chrome</li>\n<li>Responsive layout for all devices</li>\n<li>Advanced widget options</li>\n<li>Unlimited colors and over 500 Google web fonts</li>\n<li>Allow to set site title, tagline, logo and Analytics ID</li>\n<li>WPML Compatible &amp; RTL Ready</li>\n<li>Support menu with Mega and dropdown style</li>\n<li>Support primary menu location, widget sidebars</li>\n<li>6 preset Color Styles: Red, Fern, Medow, Carrot, Wisteria and Blue.</li>\n<li>Fully integrated with Font Awesome Icon</li>\n<li>Support to add custom CSS/JS</li>\n<li>Social Networks integration</li>\n<li>CSS3 table-less design</li>\n<li>LESS for advanced development</li>\n<li>Custom page templates: about us, contact us&hellip;</li>\n<li>Custom style for plugin <a href="http://contactform7.com/" rel="nofollow">Contact Form 7</a> and SEO Plugins to allow higher ranks.</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__what-are-included">WHAT ARE INCLUDED?</h3>\n<strong> Lifemag Theme Package </strong> <br> Use this package to install to your current site\n<strong> PSD Sources </strong> <br> All PSD design themes\n<strong> Detailed Documentation </strong> <br> Provide all detailed steps to configure theme\n<h3 id="item-description__need-some-help">Need some help?</h3>\nFaced a problem? No worries &ndash; our talented customer support team is always ready to help you.\nWe offer support for our customers Monday &ndash; Friday 8:30AM to 5:30PM (UTC+7). We reply on all questions within 24 hours (forums, tickets, private messages). Support request sent during weekends will be processed with the little delay.\nPlease note that the