ork with any language utilizing .PO files. Just translate the included language file and you&rsquo;re set.\n\n<h4 id="item-description__clean-code">Clean Code</h4>\nWell structured and clean code means the theme can be easily extended by any developer. We used nothing but the latest features of WordPress.\n\n<h4 id="item-description__amazing-support">Amazing Support</h4>\nWe will catch all your requests, via email, support system, Twitter or Facebook and respond to it. Included are also themes documentation and knowledge base, which will help you to find required answers as well.\n\n<h4 id="item-description__detailed-psd-files-included">Detailed PSD Files Included</h4>\nPhotoshop files are included in the theme package if you need to do any customization on theme design.\n\n<h4 id="item-description__detailed-psd-files-included">Detailed PSD Files Included</h4>\nPhotoshop files are included in the theme package if you need to do any customization on theme design.<br><h2 id="item-description__change-log">Change log</h2>\n<pre>\nVersion 1.0.5 (March 27, 2015)\n- Fixed issue with customizer\n- Changed files: inc/customizer.php\n\nVersion 1.0.4 (March 26, 2015)\n- Fixed image and layout issues on front page template\n- Integrated Tickera\nChanged files: templates/contents/content-gallery.php, templates/contents/content-event.php, style.css, inc/plugin-activation.php\n\nVersion 1.0.2 (March 25, 2015)\n- Fixed issue with event end/start date fields in admin panel\n- Files changed: inc/tk-functions.php\n\nVersion 1.0.1 (March 23, 2015)\n- Fixed issue with custom header not working on some servers\n- Files changed: header.php\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id="item-description__what-people-say-about-themes-kingdom">What people say about Themes Kingdom</h2>\n\n	<strong>Micha Karmann</strong><br>\nGuys &hellip; you&rsquo;re FANTASTIC! AWESOME!!! THIS is what I call support. One of the best here at ThemeForest. Maybe the best. THANX!!!<br><br>\n\n\n	<strong>Nicole Allison</strong><br>\nThe exp