(149, 216, 'Fri Mar 20 08:35:48 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 26 00:28:37 +1100 2015', 'frida-a-sweet-classic-blog-theme', 'Frida - A Sweet & Classic Blog Theme', 'Frida can be serious too!<br><a href="http://www.burnhambox.com/frida/?view=serious" rel="nofollow">http://www.burnhambox.com/frida/?view=serious</a>\n\n\n	Hide zig-zag effects if you wish:<br><a href="http://www.burnhambox.com/frida/?zigzag=hide" rel="nofollow">http://www.burnhambox.com/frida/?zigzag=hide</a>\n\n\n	A couple of screenshots from customizer:<br><a href="http://www.burnhambox.com/frida/customizer-screenshots/" rel="nofollow">http://www.burnhambox.com/frida/customizer-screenshots/</a>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__v-1-4-release-notes">v.1.4 Release Notes</h3>\n\n<li><strong>Sticky Header</strong> option has been added.</li>\n<li><strong>Image Widget</strong> has been improved. Now you can add a text, change text/title colors, use a color instead of image and set the height of the widget.</li>\n<li>Minor CSS fixings.</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__about-frida">About Frida</h3>\n\n	We crafted Frida in the name of sweetness! Its zig-zag theme and pastel tones take your content and turn it to a candybar itself.\n\n\n	But do you want a cleaner view? No problem for Frida. We used WordPress&rsquo; native customizer and organized it very well to let you personalize almost everything with only a few clicks.\n\n\n	Our job was not done with design only. In the groundwork, we added details and details to make Frida perfectly meet the requirements for not only personal usage, but also commercial.\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__top-features">Top Features</h3>\n\n<li><strong>Post Format Based Sidebar:</strong> You can hide the sidebar on gallery posts for example.</li>\n<li><strong>Post Format Based Stylizing:</strong> You want to display video posts in a different way maybe? Just do it!</li>\n<li><strong>Page Based Sidebar:</strong> It&rsquo;s just one click away to hide the sidebar on pages.</li>\n<li><strong>Translation via Customizer:</strong> You don&rsquo;t need to get drowned in strange language files.</li>\n<li>Responsive</li>\n<li>Very Well Organized Customizer</li>\n<li>Show/Hide/Change Almost Everything</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__other-features">Other Features</h3>\n\n<li>Classic Blog Layout</li>\n<li><strong>Unlimited Color Options</strong></li>\n<li>5 Different Layout Options</li>\n<li>Fullwidth Layout Option</li>\n<li>4 Different Header Views (Including Banner View)</li>\n<li><strong>5 Post Formats:</strong> Standard, Gallery, Video, Aside and Link</li>\n<li><strong>6 Custom Widgets:</strong> Image Widget, Popular Posts Widget, Recent Posts Widget, Recent Comments Widget, Facebook Widget and Empty Space Widget</li>\n<li>Instagram Feed</li>\n<li>18 Social Accounts Available</li>\n<li>Support for Contact Form 7</li>\n<li>SEO Optimized</li>\n<li>W3C Validated</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__coming-soon">Coming Soon!</h3>\n\n	Here&rsquo;s a small list of what we&rsquo;re planning to do in next updates.\n\n\n<li>Slider at Home Page</li>\n<li>Sticky Header (Done in v.1.4)</li>\n<li>Sticky Sidebar</li>\n<li>Font Options</li>\n<li>Improved Image Widget (Done in v.1.4)</li>\n<li>More Widget Areas</li>\n<li>Google Maps</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__need-support">Need Support?</h3>\n\n	Please don&rsquo;t hesitate to ask anything. We&rsquo;re ready to help you on our comments page! For further assistance, head over to <a href="http://burnhambox.ticksy.com" rel="nofollow">http://burnhambox.ticksy.com</a> and open a ticket.', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10623362-frida-a-sweet-classic-blog-theme', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127682565/frida-preview-v14.__large_preview.jpg', 'http://themeforest.net/item/frida-a-sweet-classic-blog-theme/10623362', 'http://themeforest.net/item/frida-a-sweet-classic-blog-theme/full_screen_preview/10623362', 38, 'art, blogging, butique, clean, colorful, cooking, craft, creative, fashion, feminine, modern, personal, pretty, si