(185, 218, 'Mon Mar 23 22:34:37 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 26 01:07:33 +1100 2015', 'android-news-app', 'Android News App', '<h3 id="item-description__android-news-app">Android News App</h3>\n \nAndroid News App is a mobile news system which run under Android platform that used for your own news application. With powerful and Responsive Admin Panel can manage news category, news item, app profile information, change admin username and password with generate password, etc. This application created by Android for client side and then PHP MySQL for Admin side. Run under Android platform which is the most popular operating system in the world. Using this application you can save your money and time in creating application for your own news application.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features</h3>\n \nDemo APK (Client Side)\n<a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/ej3agysj2mvxlmv/Android%20News%20App.apk?dl=0" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://testing.000space.com/image_news/demo%20apk.png"></a>\n<br>Demo Admin Panel (Server Side)\n<a href="http://news.dimasword.com" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://testing.000space.com/image_news/demo%20admin.png"></a>\n<br>Username : admin\n<br>Password : admin\n\n	<br><img src="http://testing.000space.com/image_news/description1.png"><br><br><img src="http://testing.000space.com/image_news/description2.png"><br><br><img src="http://news.dimasword.com/images/description0.png"><br><br><img src="http://testing.000space.com/image_news/description3.png"><br>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__what-you-get">What You Get :</h3>\n \n<li>Full Android Source Code</li>\n<li>Full Php Code of Server Side</li>\n<li>Package hierarchy (Tells which class is used for what)</li>\n<li>Full Documentation with Screenshot</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__change-log">Change Log</h3>\n \nAndroid News App V1.2\n<li>Add Parse Push Notification</li>\n<li>Add Refresh Menu</li>\n<li>Add AdMob Interstitial ads</li>\n<li>Manually Disable/Enable Date Display in News List (Incl