(452, 227, 'Mon Mar 23 19:21:10 +1100 2015', 'Mon Mar 23 19:21:10 +1100 2015', 'side-scrolling-game-template', 'Side-scrolling game template', 'Costs 1 pack of cigarettes &ndash; little to no money.<br>\nIf you want to support the work of an indie developer, sole proprietor, this is a great chance to do so.<br>\nTook me over a month to develop it and write the documentation &ndash; I think it is worth the money.<br>\nYou can use it to make your game on your website or publish on facebook.<br>\nThe template is good for learning too, if you want to learn Flash or programming basics &ndash; all well commented.<br>\n\n\n	I plan to add many more items, templates and assets and graphics in the future of games of mine that have had great interest &ndash; 3-4 million plays &ndash; here is one <a href="http://www.y8.com/games/headsmashing_world_cup" rel="nofollow">http://www.y8.com/games/headsmashing_world_cup</a> &ndash; 2 700 000 plays and counting on y8.com ONLY. Imagine if you have ads on a game like this one( I have summed at least 10 million plays on the major portals&hellip; and I  plan to offer the source code for 10-12 USD here.<br>\n\n\n	Let&rsquo;s have <strong>THIS</strong> template at least <strong>50 sales</strong> and I will upload 10 more templates.<br>\n\n\n<a href="http://pavel-nedelchev.com/" rel="nofollow">http://pavel-nedelchev.com/</a>\n\n<h2 id="item-description__cheers-p-n">Cheers!<br>\nP.N.<br></h2>	<strong>GAME INFORMATION</strong><br>\nThis is a side-scrolling jumping game template.<br>\nCoded in AS3.0 OOP.<br>\nWorks with Flash CS 4/5/5.5/6;<br>\nAll elements are easy to edit directly in the Flash IDE.<br>\nThe character parts can be replaced once, and all changes will take place in the rest animation states (running, single jump, double jump, slip, crash, falling, end).\nThere are 3 main obstacles (randomly generated):<br>\n&ndash; big block (can become chimney) &ndash; triggers END animation;<br>\n&ndash; medium block (can be bricks for example) &ndash; triggers CRASH animation;<br>\n&ndash; small block (can become puddle or ice) &ndash; triggers SLIP animation;<br>\nThe floor elements are with random length, constructed from instances of the object &ldquo;groundPart&rdquo;.<br>\nThe speed of the game is increased by each passed block.<br>\nThe background contains 4 layers, moving with different speed (making the optical illusion of movement):<br>\n&ndash; moon/sun layer &ndash; low speed;<br>\n&ndash; sky layer &ndash; higher speed;<br>\n&ndash; clouds layer &ndash; even higher speed;<br>\n&ndash; buildings layer &ndash; highest speed;<br>\nUsing the UP-ARROW key OR clicking with the mouse ONCE, will trigger the SINGLE jump.<br>\nUsing the UP-ARROW key OR clicking with the mouse TWICE, will trigger the DOUBLE jump.<br>\nThe sounds and sound control are in their own class.<br>\nThere is a preloader on Frame 1. All dynamic classes are exported in Frame 2 &ndash; ensures accurate preloader loading.<br>\nThe distribution version (which you will get by purchasing this item) includes a demo example of a game created with this template.<br>\nThe original file is with resolution 800&times;600, but the template can be made to fit any resolution.<br>\nWell-documented PDF file is attached, which contains detailed information how to fill the template.<br>\n\n\n\n	<strong>WHY SHOULD YOU BUY THIS TEMPLATE?</strong><br>\nThis template can become a beautiful and funny little game on your website (imagine your boss as the character &ndash; running from bill papers with feet, your chubby friend running to get some sandwiches?&hellip; you can share it on Facebook&hellip;how fun would that be?!) .\n\n\n	<strong>YOU WANT THE TEMPLATE, BUT DO NOT HAVE A DESIGNER TO CREATE THE GRAPHICS?</strong><br>\nWhy not&hellip; hire me&hellip;?\n\n\n	<strong>WHAT ELSE CAN YOU DO WITH THIS TEMPLATE?</strong><br>\n&ndash; You can import Starling Framework (the code has to be slightly edited &ndash; libraries are very similar, using Stage3D will allow the full potential of the hardware acceleration &ndash; CPU &amp; GPU) , generate an AIR document, add a certificate and distribute your cross-platform game &ndash; which will work on Android and iOS devices.\n\n\n	<strong>For more information</strong><br><a href="http://pavel-nedelchev.com/portfolio-item/side-scrolling-jumping-template/" rel="nofollow">CLICK HERE</a>', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127207583/preview.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/sidescrolling-game-template/10873481', '', 12, 'action, addictive, arcade, as3, blocks, easy, endless, fun, game, jump, keyboard, mouse, scrolling, side, template', 0, 0, 0);
