(465, 227, 'Fri Feb 27 19:21:14 +1100 2015', 'Mon Mar 09 19:16:34 +1100 2015', 'xml-image-viewer-rotating-slides', 'XML Image Viewer (Rotating Slides)', 'This is an advanced image viewer, that is created by using Flash CS4 and AS3&hellip;\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__features">Features:</h2>\n\n\n	1. Editable XML driven gallery.\n\n\n	2. Auto generated photo URLs (jpg, bmp, gif, png).\n\n\n	3. You can add as many presets/albums as you wish.\n\n\n	4. A unique set of parameters for obtaining the most desired animations.\n\n\n	5. Many ways/controls for playing slides.\n\n\n	6. Fully responsive to your screen resolution and when displayed in full screen.\n\n\n	7. Fully commented simple editable .fla file.\n\n\n	8. No external class files, coded inside Flash CS4 timeline.\n\n\n	9. Excel (.xlxs) file included for making it easy to create new presets.\n\n\n	10. Can be edited in 4 easy steps to change it to any banner resolution.\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__control-of-slides">Control of Slides:</h2>\n\n\n	<pre>A. using arrow keys..\nB. using mouse wheel..\nC. using click and drag..\nD. using autoplay..\nE. using navigation buttons..\nF. clicking on the slide..\nG. clicking on the top most slide, enlarges it..</pre>\n\n\n	If help requested, I will gladly present <img src="/images/smileys/happy.png" alt=":)" title=":)">', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/125345070/preview.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/xml-image-viewer-rotating-slides/10524739', 'http://activeden.net/item/xml-image-viewer-rotating-slides/full_screen_preview/10524739', 8, 'animated, as3, banner, flash, gallery, image, photo, resizable, responsive, rotating, simple, slide, template, viewer, xml', 0, 0, 0),
