(469, 227, 'Tue Feb 24 19:23:10 +1100 2015', 'Tue Feb 24 19:23:10 +1100 2015', 'planeswar-game', 'PlanesWar Game', 'Full coded in ActionScript 3.0 game with all the data from xml file.\nThe idea is simple and clean, using the old concept and rules of plane game and our own design and functionality we created a functional game that can be easy to use and configure. Anything can be changed so if you don&rsquo;t like any design I add to the game just change it using the xml file easy and simple.\nThe game rules are simple, the player and computer have to place his planes on the table and start shooting trying to destroy the opponent planes. \nYou will find a full game documentation on how to use and configure the game.\n\n\n	Visitors: <img src="http://hitwebcounter.com/counter/counter.php?page=5992799&amp;style=0008&amp;nbdigits=5&amp;type=ip&amp;initCount=0" alt="installing easiest cool counters" title="installing easiest cool counters">', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/123679656/preview.png', 'http://activeden.net/item/planeswar-game/10527602', 'http://activeden.net/item/planeswar-game/full_screen_preview/10527602', 10, 'action, actionscript, flash, game, plane, plane game, planes, play, war, war game, xml', 0, 0, 0),
