(473, 227, 'Mon Feb 23 18:37:19 +1100 2015', 'Tue Feb 24 19:03:41 +1100 2015', 'bubbles-crash-game', 'Bubbles Crash Game', 'Bubbles Crash &ndash; bright bubbles game with various levels.\nYou have to poke bubbles groups with the same color near to crash and destroy them. The more bubbles will be crashed at once &ndash; the more points you get. You have to reach target score on each level to pass mission. The game has 40 levels.\n\n\n	- The demo of working Android application can be found here <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.inkerapps.BubblesCrash" rel="nofollow">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.inkerapps.BubblesCrash</a> \n- Video demo of gameplay can be found here <a href="http://youtu.be/jb4xUUfIiPY" rel="nofollow">http://youtu.be/jb4xUUfIiPY</a>\n\n\n	While playing Bubbles Crash game you will face such challenges:\n- Target score will get higher\n- New bubble colors will be added\n- New lines with colorful bubbles will appear\n\n\n	Main Bubbles Crash bubbles game features:\n- just fun way to spend time\n- bright and colorful graphics\n- unique 3D bubbles of different shape and color\n- 40 various levels and missions\n- your progress and stars for all levels are saved\n- suits for people with eyes problems as all bubbles have different shape\n\n\n	In Bubbles Crash game you can get 1, 2 or 3 stars after passing each mission.\n\n\n	To get 1 star you just have to reach target bubbles score for this level\nTo get 2 stars you have to reach target bubbles score +10% for the level\nTo get 3 stars you have to reach target bubbles score +20% for the level\n\n\n	Development features:\n- Prepared for building Android and iOS apps (using Adobe Air)\n- AdMob ANE is included and configured to show your banners and fullscreen ads after each level\n- Target scores, bubbles colors, number of bubble lines can be easily configured for each level\n- The game progress and scores are saved and loaded\n- Bubbles images and backgrounds can be easily changed', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/123656530/preview.swf', 'http://activeden.net/item/bubbles-crash-game/10489868', '', 10, 'admob, air, ane, balls, bright, bubbles game, bubbles poke, casual, customizable, levels, puzzle, resizable', 0, 0, 0),
