(477, 227, 'Thu Feb 19 20:04:44 +1100 2015', 'Thu Feb 19 20:04:44 +1100 2015', 'galaxy-web-banners', 'Galaxy Web Banners', 'new advertising banner set for your website. Very unique and creative. Google ad-words ready click tag. Available in different and new Google sizes.\n\n\n	300&times;250 Also known as a &ldquo;medium rectangle&rdquo;. Tends to have more ad inventory available from advertisers, which can increase earnings when both text and image ads are enabled.\n\n\n	336&times;280 &acirc;&#128;&nbsp; Also known as a &ldquo;large rectangle&rdquo;. Tends to have more ad inventory available from advertisers, which can increase earnings when both text and image ads are enabled.\n\n\n	728&times;90 Also known as a &ldquo;leaderboard&rdquo;. Tends to have more ad inventory available from advertisers, which can increase earnings when both text and image ads are enabled.\n\n\n	160&times;600 Also known as a &ldquo;wide skyscraper&rdquo;. Tends to have more ad inventory available from advertisers, which can increase earnings when both text and image ads are enabled.\n\n\n	468&times;60 Also known as a &ldquo;banner&rdquo;. This format can fit into smaller spaces that don&rsquo;t accommodate the 728&times;90 leaderboard.\n\n\n	120&times;600 Also known as a &ldquo;skyscraper&rdquo;, this format can fit into narrower spaces that don&rsquo;t accommodate the 160&times;600 wide skyscraper.\n\n\n	250&times;250 Also known as a &ldquo;square&rdquo;, this format can fit into smaller spaces that don&rsquo;t accommodate the larger rectangles.\n\n\n	200&times;200 Also known as a &ldquo;small square&rdquo;, this format can fit into smaller spaces that don&rsquo;t accommodate the larger rectangles.\n\n\n	180&times;150 Also known as a &ldquo;small rectangle&rdquo;, this format can fit into small spaces.\n\n\n	980&times;120 Also known as a &ldquo;panorama&rdquo;. Most popular size in Sweden and Finland. Can also be used as a substitute in Norway.\n\n\n	930&times;180 Also known as a &ldquo;