(503, 228, 'Sat Mar 31 03:12:04 +1100 2012', 'Sat Mar 31 03:12:04 +1100 2012', 'advanced-3d-showcase', 'Advanced 3D Showcase', '<strong>Features:</strong>\nThis application show you the image cube in 3d view with rotation we can use this application for  multi purpose ex: new product arrival,e-Commerce etc&hellip;\nWhen you click the particular object it will enlarge again if you click it will go to the same possession. And please view in full screen and test all the controls- you can see in the right side of application.\n\nAlso you can\n<br>1. Add\n<br>2. Remove\n<br>3. Zoom\n<br>4. Minimize\n<br>5. Maximize\n<strong>Settings:</strong>\n<br>1. Show grid\n<br>2. Docking distance\n<br>3. Pan\n<br>4. Tilt\n<br>5. Item rotation x\n<br>6. Row count\n<br>7. Horizontal gap\n<br>8. Radios\n<br>from the right side bar and much more&hellip;.\n\nSS 1:\n<img src="http://richapplication.com/data//uploads/items/29/preview/preview.jpg"><br>SS 2:\n<img src="http://richapplication.com/data//uploads/items/29/preview/preview2.jpg"><br>SS 3:\n<img src="http://richapplication.com/data//uploads/items/29/preview/preview3.jpg"><br>SS 4:\n<img src="http://richapplication.com/data//uploads/items/29/preview/preview4.jpg"><br>SS 5:\n<img src="http://richapplication.com/data//uploads/items/29/preview/preview5.jpg">', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/23275085/preview.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/advanced-3d-showcase/2007924', 'http://activeden.net/item/advanced-3d-showcase/full_screen_preview/2007924', 13, '3d showcase, 3d template, flex 3d rotate, flex effects, flex showcase, flex template', 0, 0, 0),
(504, 228, 'Wed Apr 11 16:56:11 +1000 2012', 'Thu Oct 11 17:34:35 +1100 2012', 'helptipshow-interactive-help-tips-for-your-app', 'HelpTipShow - interactive help tips for your app', '<strong>HelpTipShow</strong> &ndash; is a component that allows you easy adding interactive help tips to your application. With this you can easly guide your appliction users how to use the application user interface elements. It&rsquo;s fully customizable, allows for creating modal or nonmodal help tip shows.\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__easy-way-to-add-to-your-project">Easy way to add to your project:</h3>\nJust put into declaration tags or create object programmatically than call play() method and it&rsquo;s done.\n<pre>\n &lt;-- component --&gt;\n &lt;fpria:HelpTipShow id="myShow" &gt;\n   &lt;fx:Vector type="flexphperia.components.supportClasses.HelpTip"&gt;\n\n    &lt;-- first help tip --&gt;\n    &lt;fpria:HelpTip duration="3500" element="{buttonInstance}" \n                   textHorizontalPosition="onLeft" \n                   textVerticalPosition="above" \n                   verticalOffset="15" &gt;\n\n      &lt;s:p&gt;This is description for a element.&lt;/s:p&gt;         \n\n    &lt;/fpria:HelpTip&gt;\n\n   &lt;-- second help tip --&gt;\n    &lt;fpria:HelpTip duration="4500" element="{anotherInstance}" \n                   textHorizontalPosition="center" \n                   textVerticalPosition="below" \n                   verticalOffset="35" &gt;\n\n      &lt;s:p&gt;This is another description for an another element.&lt;/s:p&gt;         \n\n    &lt;/fpria:HelpTip&gt;\n\n   &lt;/fx:Vector&gt;\n &lt;/fpria:HelpTipShow&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features:</h3>\n<li>configurable time that help tip is displayed and it&rsquo;s position</li>\n<li>use Text Layout Framework to create help tip description so you can easly stylize  your text</li>\n<li>designed in Flex 4, fully skinnable in Spark skinning architecture</li>\n<li>ready to use SWC library include