(572, 231, 'Wed Mar 18 09:28:56 +1100 2015', 'Fri Mar 20 07:20:36 +1100 2015', 'slider-responsive-media-driven-ghost-theme', 'Slider - Responsive, Media Driven Ghost Theme', '<a href="http://themeforest.net/user/7immer/follow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/BCdytGI.jpg" alt="follow us"></a>\n    <a href="http://themeforest.net/user/7immy"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/c7HMK5C.jpg" alt="get help"></a>\n<br><a href="http://www.tricider.com/brainstorming/2jnbLkLgo4N" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/BuxvBbe.jpg" alt="request features"></a>\n<br>Slider. The multi-purpose, media driven, responsive theme for the <a href="https://ghost.org" rel="nofollow">Ghost blogging platform</a>. Slider is a perfectly tailored template for headline grabbing blogs, eye catching portfolios and your ideal music or video blog.\n\n\nMake every post or portfolio item you make stand out with our highly customisable title covers supporting multiple layouts, styles and embedded media like youtube, Soundcloud, Vimeo or anything else you fancy.\n\nWith smooth animations and ajax page transitions your users will glide through your website with ease.\n\nOn top of all that Slider comes packed with extra features like contact forms tag page listings, author page listings and google maps. All can be easily added with a simple markdown tag.\n\nSlider is fully responsive with great cross-browser support and backwards compatibility across all major browsers!\n\nEnjoy great customisability.\n<br><br><h3 id="item-description__smooth-gliding-transitions">SMOOTH GLIDING TRANSITIONS</h3>\nLet your users glide through every post and page with smooth animations and ajax page transitions.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/saxvIVp.gif" alt="smooth gliding transitions"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__impactful-title-covers">IMPACTFUL TITLE COVERS</h3>\nMake every post or portfolio item you make stand out with our highly customisable title covers. Choose from multiple layout styles, and font-sizes and colours and tailor your backgrounds to be fixed colours or colourful images. Add media like images videos audio or embedded content and of course you can customise each post separately.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/eUab27I.gif" alt="impactful title covers"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__built-in-contact-form-with-odamae">BUILT-IN CONTACT FORM WITH ODAMAE</h3>\nOne thing ghost lacks is an easy to use contact form. Now with Odamae Slider provides just that.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/lV7Mp73.jpg" alt="built-in contact form"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__fully-responsive-template">FULLY RESPONSIVE TEMPLATE</h3>\nYou never know what screen screen your website will be on so we&rsquo;ve design slider to be responsive from the biggest screens all the way down to on-the-go mobile users.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/MRCjgc0.gif" alt="fully responsive template"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__embed-anything-anywhere-build-smashing-cover-titles">EMBED ANYTHING ANYWHERE &ndash; BUILD SMASHING COVER TITLES</h3>\nSlider lets you add any kind of media to your cover titles and posts be it images, video, audio or an embed. Slider&rsquo;s ability to embed any kind of media makes this the perfect template for media based bloggers. Whether you&rsquo;re promoting products, music, design work, animations or anything else you can think of.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/uy14Kwf.gif" alt="embed anything anywhere"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__create-variable-post-image-sizes-with-your-markdown">CREATE VARIABLE POST IMAGE SIZES WITH YOUR MARKDOWN</h3>\nSlider enables you yo emphasises your posts images for greater impact with readers. This also allows you to greater customise your posts if you for example are writing a case study on your latest creative portfolio work.\n\n	<img src="http://i.imgur.com/mMj34TH.gif" alt="create variable post image sizes"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__auto-detecting-syntax-highlighter">AUTO DETECTING SYNTAX HIGHLIGHTER</h3>\nCoders rejoice! Slider comes built in with an auto detecting syntax highlighter built by <a href="https://highlightjs.org/" rel="nofollow">highlightjs</a>. It detects hundreds of languages and comes with many styles.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/lcpT4o9.jpg" alt="auto detecting syntax highlighter"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__easy-colour-font-and-border-customisations-with-scss">EASY COLOUR, FONT AND BORDER CUSTOMISATIONS WITH SCSS</h3>\nLove the template but need to use your own colours and fonts? Simple. Just use SCSS&rsquo;s variables and customise to your liking.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/W8SFsyc.jpg" alt="colour customisable"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__choose-between-standard-and-mobile-menus">CHOOSE BETWEEN STANDARD AND MOBILE MENUS</h3>\nBy default Slider will automatically change from a standard menu display to a mobile menu display depending on your browsers size. However if you love the simplicity of the mobile menu Slider give you the option to only show that instead.\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/B27bZIX.jpg" alt="standard and mobile menus"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__auto-generate-all-tags-with-a-simple-markdown-tag">AUTO GENERATE ALL TAGS WITH A SIMPLE MARKDOWN TAG</h3>\nGhost currently has no built in site wide tag list but this is not the case with Slider! Slider not only has a tag menu but also enables you to stylishly add a tag list to any page with a simple markdown tag meaning tag list pages are now possible!\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/YVJocTN.jpg" alt="auto generate all tags list"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__auto-generate-author-list-with-a-simple-markdown-tag">AUTO GENERATE AUTHOR LIST WITH A SIMPLE MARKDOWN TAG</h3>\nGhost currently has no built in site wide author list but this is not the case with Slider! With Slider you can add a simple markdown tag to any page meaning author lists pages are now possible!\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/ulw0MWY.jpg" alt="auto generate all authors list"><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__just-a-few-extras">JUST A FEW EXTRAS</h3>\nHere are just a few extras\n<img src="http://i.imgur.com/obR0lgk.jpg" alt="lots of extras"><h3 id="item-description__changes">CHANGES</h3>\n<pre>\n19.03.2015 v1.0.1\n---Scroll issue with some elements on a post page on iPhones\n\n03.14.2015 v1.0.0\n---Released\n</pre>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__credits">CREDITS</h3>\n1. Javascript\nSlider uses several great scripts to enhance this site. Thanks to all these developers:\n<li><a href="https://github.com/jquery/jquery" rel="nofollow">jQuery</a></li>\n    <li><a href="https://github.com/davatron5000/FitVids.js" rel="nofollow">FitVids.js</a></li>\n    <li><a href="https://github.com/browserstate/history.js" rel="nofollow">jQuery history</a></li>\n    <li><a href="https://highlightjs.org/" rel="nofollow">highlight.js</a></li>\n    <li><a href="http://labs.rampinteractive.co.uk/touchSwipe/demos/" rel="nofollow">touchSwipe</a></li>\n    <li><a href="http://noraesae.github.io/perfect-scrollbar/" rel="nofollow">Perfect Scrollbar</a></li>\n    <li><a href="http://ricostacruz.com/nprogress/" rel="nofollow">NProgress.js</a></li>\n2. Stylesheets\nSlider uses this great stylesheet to enhance this theme. Thanks to this developer:\n<li><a href="https://github.com/necolas/normalize.css" rel="nofollow">normalize.css</a></li>\n3. Images\nImages shown on the live demo are from <a href="http://unsplash.com/" rel="nofollow">www.unsplash.com</a>. As a precaution we have not included the images shown on the live demo in this download, however feel free to download their great selection of public domain photos.\n \n4. Fonts and Icons\n<li>Google Webfonts &ndash; <a href="https://www.google.com/fonts" rel="nofollow">https://www.google.com/fonts</a></li>\n    <li>Font Awesome &ndash; <a href="http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/" rel="nofollow">http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/</a></li>\n<h3 id="item-description__feature-requests">FEATURE REQUESTS</h3>\nIf you would like to make a feature request please use the form via <a href="http://www.tricider.com/brainstorming/2jnbLkLgo4N" rel="nofollow">this link</a>. To increase your chances of development please included a reason to why you think your request should be added to this theme.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__support">Support</h3>\nThe documentation included in the download provides helpful step by step guides to get your theme installed and customised. If you would like any further advice just send us an email via the <a href="http://themeforest.net/user/7immer">profile page</a>.\n\nIf you have any bug reports please let us know!', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10771699-slider-responsive-media-driven-ghost-theme', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/126176343/preview.__large_preview.jpg', 'http://themeforest.net/item/slider-responsive-media-driven-ghost-theme/10771699', 'http://themeforest.net/item/slider-responsive-media-driven-ghost-theme/full_screen_preview/10771699', 24, 'ajax, animation, blog, clean, flat, fluid, ghost, media, modern, personal, responsive, simple, slider, social, syntax', 0, 0, 0),
