(582, 231, 'Thu Feb 26 15:50:27 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 19 10:34:16 +1100 2015', 'hybrid-a-modern-grid-theme-for-ghost', 'HYBRID - A Modern Grid Theme For Ghost', '\n<a href="http://eepurl.com/xchRP" rel="nofollow">\n        <img src="http://www.sunflowertheme.com/assets/img/promote/dragonfly/wordpress-v-banner.png"></a>\n\n    \n    <a href="http://themeforest.net/user/sunflowertheme/follow">\n        <img src="http://www.sunflowertheme.com/assets/img/promote/vone/tf.png"></a>\n    <a href="https://twitter.com/sunflowertheme" rel="nofollow">\n        <img src="http://www.sunflowertheme.com/assets/img/promote/vone/twitter.png"></a>    \n\n\n    <strong>HYBRID is a Modern Grid Theme for Ghost. It was designed for readability on all devices. It can be used as a blog, personal store, portfolio, journal and it&rsquo;s very easy to setup and use.</strong>\n\n\n    <strong>Let&rsquo;s look at HYBRID Features and choose it for your site.</strong>\n\n\n    <img src="http://previews.sunflowertheme.com/ghost/hybrid/assets/img/screenshot.jpg" alt="Screenshot">\n\n    <a href="http://hybrid-style1.sunflowertheme.com" rel="nofollow">    \n        <img src="http://previews.sunflowertheme.com/ghost/hybrid/assets/img/demo1.jpg" alt="Demo Style #1"></a>    \n    <a href="http://hybrid-style2.sunflowertheme.com" rel="nofollow">\n        <img src="http://previews.sunflowertheme.com/ghost/hybrid/assets/img/demo2.jpg" alt="Demo Style #2"></a>\n    <a href="http://hybrid-style3.sunflowertheme.com" rel="nofollow">\n        <img src="http://previews.sunflowertheme.com/ghost/hybrid/assets/img/demo3.jpg" alt="Demo Style #3"></a>\n    <a href="http://hybrid-style4.sunflowertheme.com" rel="nofollow">\n        <img src="http://previews.sunflowertheme.com/ghost/hybrid/assets/img/demo4.jpg" alt="Demo Style #4"></a>\n    <a href="http://hybrid-style5.sunflowertheme.com" rel="nofollow">\n        <img src="http://previews.sunflowertheme.com/ghost/hybrid/assets/img/demo5.jpg" alt="Demo Style #5"></a>\n