ort</li>    \n    <li>And much more &hellip;</li>\n<h2 id="item-description__customer-reviews">Customer Reviews:</h2>\n\n    <img src="http://www.sunflowertheme.com/assets/img/promote/dragonfly/rating.png" alt="Buyer said"><img src="http://www.sunflowertheme.com/assets/img/promote/dragonfly/rate.png" alt="Rate">\n<h2 id="item-description__have-a-question">Have a question?</h2>\n\n    <strong>You are not only buying this theme but also bought our support, we are here to help so drop us a line if you need assistance.</strong>\n\n\n    The documentation included provides all the information needed to get the theme installed and customized. However, if you have any questions you can <a href="http://themeforest.net/user/sunflowertheme"><strong>contact us via profile page here</strong></a>, and we will be happy to help.\n\n<h2 id="item-description__change-logs">Change Logs</h2>\n<pre>\n03/19/2015 v1.1.0\n    ==&gt; Add Ghost Built-in Navigation support\n    ==&gt; Add Magnific image preview support\n    ==&gt; Optimize Newsletter widget\n    ==&gt; Update documentation\n02/24/2015 v1.0.0\n    ==&gt; Initial Release 1.0.0\n</pre>\n<h2 id="item-description__credits">Credits</h2>        \n<strong>JavaScript</strong>\nHybrid uses several scripts many of which are documented within the theme&rsquo;s code. If you&rsquo;re a developer, you will find this particularly useful.\n<li>\n        <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/" rel="nofollow">Bootstrap Framework</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveRaven/jqBootstrapValidation" rel="nofollow">\n            jQuery Bootstrap Validation\n        </a>\n    </li>                    \n    <li>\n        <a href="http://fitvidsjs.com/" rel="nofollow">\n            FitVids\n        </a>\n    </li>    \n    <li>\n        <a href="http://desandro.github.io/imagesloaded/" rel="nofollow">\n            imagesLoaded\n        </a>\n    </li>                    \n    <li>\n        <a href="http://dimsemenov.com/plugin