(585, 231, 'Tue Feb 17 12:37:09 +1100 2015', 'Tue Feb 24 00:50:52 +1100 2015', 'caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme', 'Caesar - A Clean and Focused Theme', '<strong>A clean and focused theme for Ghost. Includes four colour schemes to kick start customisation.</strong>\n\nAn ideal theme for minimalists or lovers of whitespace. Show off latest posts, Dribbble Shots or Instagram Photos! Let visitors comment on your posts with Disqus Comments or share them with Shares.\n\n<strong>Post Types</strong>\n\nIncludes support for <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/herobust-party-mcfly/" rel="nofollow">Audio</a>, <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/chat/" rel="nofollow">Chat</a>, <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/mikedidthis-themeforest-profile/" rel="nofollow">Link</a>, <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/a-knot-wallpaper/" rel="nofollow">Photo</a>, <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/quote-by-seneca/" rel="nofollow">Quote</a> and <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/mr-selfie/" rel="nofollow">Video</a> posts types.\n\n<strong>Page Types</strong>\n\nIncludes support for <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/author/mike/" rel="nofollow">Author</a>, <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/about/" rel="nofollow">Static</a> and <a href="http://demos.mikedidthis.co.uk/ghost-caesar/tag/article/" rel="nofollow">Tag</a> Pages.\n\n<strong>Skins</strong>\n\nChoose from <a href="http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10378083-caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme?index=1&amp;url_name=caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme">Default</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10378083-caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme?index=2&amp;url_name=caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme">Gallery</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10378083-caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme?index=3&amp;url_name=caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme">Blueprint</a> or <a href="http://themefore