edidthis.co.uk</a>.\n\n<strong>Tumblr Version</strong>\n\nThe Tumblr version of this theme is available from <a href="https://www.tumblr.com/theme/39606" rel="nofollow">tumblr.com</a>.\n\n<strong>Wordpress Version</strong>\n\nThe Wordpress version of this theme is available from <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/caesar-a-clean-and-focused-wordpress-blog-theme/10570481">themeforest.com</a>.', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10378083-caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/123572193/01_promo.__large_preview.png', 'http://themeforest.net/item/caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme/10378083', 'http://themeforest.net/item/caesar-a-clean-and-focused-theme/full_screen_preview/10378083', 24, 'blog, clean, desktop, disqus, dribbble, ghost, instagram, minimal, mobile, multiple skins, responsive, whitespace', 0, 0, 0),
