(587, 231, 'Thu Feb 12 18:38:19 +1100 2015', 'Fri Feb 13 00:19:16 +1100 2015', 'mocha-minimal-grid-based-template', 'Mocha: Minimal Grid-Based Template', 'Enjoy uncropped thumbnails with Mocha, a minimal portfolio template made with photographers and designers in mind. Its masonry-grid-based home page launches users directly into your work with no distraction.\n\n\n	Mocha uses template 2.0 framework with various Template Designer&acirc;&#132;&cent; options, including an option to help you change the width of your blog. It also features custom Mobile Template for better mobile browsing experience besides supporting responsive layout.\n\n\n	<strong>Demo:</strong> <a href="http://mocha-extensv.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow">Grid-based Portfolio</a> | <a href="http://mocha2-extensv.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow">Standard blog</a> | <a href="http://mocha-extensv.blogspot.com/?m=1" rel="nofollow">Mobile</a>\n\n\n	<strong>Primary Features:</strong>\n<li>Available in two styles, Portfolio and Blog</li>\n<li>Various Template Designer&acirc;&#132;&cent; options</li>\n<li>Responsive layout</li>\n<li>Custom Mobile Template support</li>\n<li>Well Google+ integrated, including: author avatar and G+ comment.</li>\n<li>Compatible with <a href="http://extensv.com/gadgets/" rel="nofollow">Extenv&rsquo;s gadgets</a> (truly XML-based gadgets): Flickr, Social buttons</li>\n<li>Well designed comment section</li>\n<li>Great typography and unique design in minimal way</li>\n<li>Selectable metadatas</li>\n<li>Extensive documentation</li>\n<li>Coded by the Expert</li>\n<strong>Template Designer&acirc;&#132;&cent;:</strong>\n<li>You can select a variety of colors and fonts.</li>\n<li>Custom background upload</li>\n<li>Layout width control</li>\n<li>Footer layout option from one to three columns</li>\n<strong>Support</strong> is conducted via <a href="http://dzignine.ticksy.com" rel="nofollow">Ticksy</a>. Simply drop a ticket in case you need a help. I do handle short question via <a href="http://twitter.com/biyanpasau" rel="nofollow">Twitter</a> as well.', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10375439-mocha-minimal-gridbased-template', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/121973090/Screenshot.__large_preview.png', 'http://themeforest.net/item/mocha-minimal-gridbased-template/10375439', 'http://themeforest.net/item/mocha-minimal-gridbased-template/full_screen_preview/10375439', 21, 'blogger, blogging, galley, grey, grid, masonry, minimal, minimalist, modern, photography, portfolio, responsive, thumbnail, white', 0, 0, 0),
(588, 231, 'Wed Feb 11 14:23:18 +1100 2015', 'Wed Feb 11 19:47:18 +1100 2015', 'fine-the-fullwidth-all-features-tumblr-theme', 'Fine - The Fullwidth All-Features Tumblr Theme', 'With a multitude of functions, FINE focuses the last post and the permalink post in a very bold way, with special attention to all types. If your website is dedicated to audio, video, or photo &ndash; or if it is a business blog &ndash; this is the Tumblr theme for you.\n\n\n	<img src="http://4.ii.gl/jQwLhI0j2.png"><a href="http://finetheme.tumblr.com/demo" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://4.ii.gl/9qRAa75G7.png"></a>\n<a href="http://finethemedocs.tumblr.com/" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://4.ii.gl/1lUc7IcS2.png"></a><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/zwuNZefly.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/7CHgM-5AE.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/Efqvw-Pt.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/mQp_x6FOz.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/Uqx60Kzhg.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/WBfccwpgU.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/vVteJKdw.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/dv-KZ1VqT.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/D7CE2_oZ.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/UCk0r5JLy.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/szyldGO9m.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/Mbrd_7yH5.png"><br><img src="http://4.ii.gl/VkPf2gAPV.png"><br><a href="http://finetheme.tumblr.com/demo" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://4.ii.gl/mLjTkZ_En.png"></a>\n<br><br>\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__features-list">Features List</h2>\n<li>Photo posts support:\n    <li>Fullwidth support (optional)</li>\n        <li>Modal window</li>\n        <li>EXIF data support (optional)</li>\n        <li>Adjusts to browser height (optional).</li>\n    </li>\n    <li>Photoset posts support:\n    <li>Slideshow display</li>\n        <li>Fullwidth support (optional)</li>\n        <li>Caption support</li>\n        <li>Autoslide (optional)</li>\n        <li>Modal window</li>\n        <li>Adjusts to browser height (optional).</li>\n    </li>\n    <li>Panorama posts support.</li>\n    <li>Video posts support:\n    <li>Fullwidth support (optional)</li>\n        <li>Native player, YouTube, Vimeo support</li>\n        <li>Responsive videos</li>\n    </li>\n    <li>Audio posts support:\n    <li>Fullwidth layout</li>\n        <li>Custom native player with optional cover image and ID3 tags support (track, artist, album)</li>\n        <li>Uses native header or extracts first image from description (optional)</li>\n        <li>External player support with download button</li>\n        <li>Fullwidth SoundCloud support.</li>\n    </li>\n    <li>Quote posts support &ndash; uses native header or extracts first image from description (optional).</li>\n    <li>Text posts support &ndash; extracts first image as post list thumbnail (optional).</li>\n    <li>Link posts support:\n    <li>With or without thumbnail</li>\n        <li>Uses native header or extracts first image from description (optional).</li>\n    </li>\n    <li>Chat posts support.</li>\n    <li>Answer posts support.</li>\n    <li>Categories menu (optional) with custom label &ndash; automatically extracts all tags.</li>\n    <li>Automatically features the latest post for each page &ndash; you can turn it off and display just a list of posts.</li>\n    <li>Instead of featured post, replace it with description and avatar (optional)</li>\n    <li>Post author display (optional) and social sharing via Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus, E-Mail, Pinterest (for photo posts).</li>\n    <li>Full group blogs support &ndash; post author display, member list on pages (optional).</li>\n    <li>Twitter feed (optional) and Facebook feed (optional) on pages.</li>\n    <li>Fully responsive layout &ndash; works on mobile, tablet and desktop devices.</li>\n    <li>Infinite scroll and normal pagination support &ndash; applies sticky on-hover footer when the Infinite Scroll option is selected.</li>\n    <li>Sticky header (optional) with color and transparency customization.</li>\n    <li>Normal Grid, Masonry Grid or List View with optional post list label.</li>\n    <li>Pages, Ask, Submit support.</li>\n    <li>Tag page support.</li>\n    <li>Adjust featured photos to the height of the browser (optional).</li>\n    <li>Preload content animation (optional).</li>\n    <li>Previous / Next / Random post links on permalink (optional).</li>\n    <li>Liked Posts support on pages (optional).</li>\n    <li>Single-click color setup.</li>\n    <li>Custom logo support (automatically resizes to a maximum height of 80px).</li>\n    <li>Color customization options, utilizes native appearance options, quickly converts to a dark theme.</li>\n    <li>Fully localized &ndash; complete control of theme language, including custom labels &acirc;&#128;&#148; English, German, French, Italian, Japanese, Turkish, Spanish, Russian, Polish, Portuguese.</li>\n    <li>Disqus comments (optional) &ndash; automatically detects blog and translates according to theme language.</li>\n    <li>Google Fonts:\n    <li>One menu for body font, one menu for quotations font.</li>\n        <li>Included fonts: Open Sans, PT Sans, Droid Sans, Noto Sans, Fira Sans, Lato, Roboto, Ubuntu, Arvo, Vesper Libre, Playfair Display, Neuton, PT Serif, Droid Serif, Noto Serif, Merriweather, Georgia, Times, Arial, Helvetica.</li>\n    </li>\n    <li>Support for Latin, Greek, Cyrillic, Vietnamese, Devanagari characters (according to font).</li>\n    <li>Social network links in footer &ndash; Facebook, Twitter, Google+, Flickr, Behance, Instagram, Dribbble, deviantArt, Pinterest, YouTube, Vimeo, SoundCloud, Linkedin.</li>\n    <li>Hide Tumblr controls on theme (optional).</li>\n    <li>Super easy documentation &ndash; visual, offline and searchable online.</li>\n    <li>12+ Live Demos, 30+ Live Accents.</li>\n', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10185519-fine-the-fullwidth-allfeatures-theme', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/122160535/00_Fine-Preview.__large_preview.jpg', 'http://themeforest.net/item/fine-the-fullwidth-allfeatures-tumblr-theme/10185519', 'http://themeforest.net/item/fine-the-fullwidth-allfeatures-theme/full_screen_preview/10185519', 32, 'agency, band, business, designer, gallery, id3, listing, movie, musician, news, photographer, portfolio, slider, writer', 0, 0, 0);
