(589, 231, 'Wed Feb 11 20:03:29 +1100 2015', 'Fri Mar 06 18:47:04 +1100 2015', 'journey-responsive-ghost-theme', 'Journey - Responsive Ghost Theme', '<strong>Journey</strong> is a responsive, modern and neat ghost theme. Its perfect for personal blogs, travel blogs, photography sites etc. With Journey&rsquo;s modern design it makes your ghost blog more live and bright. It is build on latest  boostrap framework\n\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features</h3>\n<li><strong>Ghost 0.5.10</strong>: Super latest!</li>\n<li><strong>Dynamic navigation menu</strong>: Build your nav from ghost dashboard !</li>\n<img src="http://blog.ghost.org/content/images/2015/03/nav-admin.gif"><li><strong>Multiple authors</strong></li>\n\n<li><strong>Bootstrap 3</strong>: Built with bootstrap 3</li>\n<li><strong>Tag page cover</strong>: Add different cover for your tag pages</li>\n\n<li><strong>Responsive Design</strong>: Smartphone, Tablet, PC any other machine your blog will be fit</li>\n<li><strong>Responsive videos</strong>: Integrated with fitvids</li>\n<li><strong>Feature media</strong>: Display feature media in homepage</li>\n<li><strong>Featured post</strong> : Featured post indicator</li>\n<li><strong>Font awesome</strong>: Journey is integrated with fontawesome</li>\n<li><strong>Google web fonts</strong>: Integrated with google webfonts</li>\n\n<li><strong>Social sharing</strong>: Sharing buttons below every post makes everything easy to share</li>\n<li><strong>Disqus</strong>: Integrated with disqus commenting system</li>\n<li><strong>Documentation</strong>: An help file to build your blog with Journey</li>\n<li><strong>Free support</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Much more</strong>: .....</li>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__credits">Credits</h3>\n<li><a href="http://unsplash.com" rel="nofollow">Unsplash.com</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://fitvidsjs.com" rel="nofollow">FitVids js</a></li>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__more-themes">More themes</h3>\n<a href="http://themeforest.net/item