(590, 231, 'Tue Feb 10 18:21:58 +1100 2015', 'Tue Feb 10 18:21:58 +1100 2015', 'futura-responsive-minimal-ghost-theme', 'Futura - Responsive Minimal Ghost Theme', '<strong>Futura</strong> is a clean minimal &amp; modern content focus theme for ghost blogging platform. it is 100% responsive means it will fit in various device of different size. Featuring an image or an audio or a video in your post is very simple as 1-2-3&hellip;\nUsing Futura you can setup a beautiful personal blog. This theme is multi-user ready so you can setup a multi-user blog or journal with no extra effort.  <strong>Futura</strong> is suitable for any kind of personal or travel, hobby, tutorial blog.\n\n	Installing and customizing this theme is very easy. All required information are provided in documentation.\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features</h3>\n<li>Ready for Ghost latest version &ndash; 0.5.8</li>\n<li>Widgetized sidebar and footer</li>\n<li>Re ordering or adding or removing widgets are very easy</li>\nTwo level Menu\n<li>100% responsive</li>\n<li>Multi author support</li>\n<li>Easy featured image / youtube / vimeo / soundcloud / mixcloud</li>\n<li>All youtube / vimeo / soundcloud / mixcloud are responsive</li>\n<li>Any other &lt;Iframe&gt; object from other than above can be feature media</li>\n<li>static pages</li>\n<li>Author page</li>\n<li>Tag page</li>\n<li>Mailchimp subscription</li>\n<li>Nice Code Highlighting</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility Chrome, FireFox, Safari, IE9, IE10, IE11</li>\n<li>Comment with disqus</li>\n<li>Google font</li>\n<li>Font Awesome icons (retina ready)</li>\n<li>Well commented and well structured coding</li>\n<li>LESS (CSS) file included, Easily achieve any color</li>\n<li>Easy to customize </li>\n<li>HTML5 / CSS3 valid code</li>\n<li>table less design</li>\n<li>Image less design</li>\n<li>And more&hellip;</li>\n<h3 id="item-description__attributions-amp-credits">Attributions &amp; Credits</h3>\n      <li><a href="http://fontawesome.io/