 Ghost Themes Blogging"></a>\n\n\n<a href="http://themeforest.net/item/activa-responsive-multipurpose-ghost-theme/6435728"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/WVZhIbt.png" alt="activa responsive multipurpose ghost theme"></a>\n\n\n<a href="http://themeforest.net/item/flora-responsive-timeline-ghost-theme/6361474"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/iQ3Cssu.png" alt="Flora - Responsive Timeline Ghost Theme - Ghost Themes Blogging"></a>\n\n\n<a href="http://themeforest.net/item/magma-clean-responsive-modern-ghost-theme/6264963"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/ovILXN8.png" alt="Magma - Clean Responsive Modern Ghost Theme - Ghost Themes Blogging"></a>\n', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/10330342-futura-responsive-minimal-ghost-theme', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/121425471/preview.__large_preview.png', 'http://themeforest.net/item/futura-responsive-minimal-ghost-theme/10330342', 'http://themeforest.net/item/futura-responsive-minimal-ghost-theme/full_screen_preview/10330342', 24, 'blog, clean, elegant, flat, ghost, ghost theme, minimal, mobile, modern, personal, responsive, simple, typography, video, white', 0, 0, 0),
