(592, 231, 'Wed Feb 11 08:51:45 +1100 2015', 'Mon Mar 16 13:21:23 +1100 2015', 'momentum-ghost-blog-with-masonry-layout', 'Momentum - Ghost Blog with Masonry Layout', '<strong>Momentum 1.1.1 is here!</strong><h2 id="item-description__welcome-to-momentum">Welcome to Momentum!</h2>Momentum is a Ghost Blog with Masonry Layout designed to take Ghost to the limit, comes with a ton of features, and of course a nice design. <h2 id="item-description__credits">Credits</h2> <li><a href="http://daneden.github.io/animate.css/" rel="nofollow">Animate.css</a> &ndash; Daniel Eden</li> <li><a href="http://prismjs.com/" rel="nofollow">PrismJS</a> &ndash; LeaVerou</li> <li><a href="http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/" rel="nofollow">FontAwesome</a> &ndash; Dave Gandy</li> <li><a href="http://subtlepatterns.com/" rel="nofollow">Dark Sharp Edges</a> &ndash; Carlos Aguilar</li> <li><a href="http://fitvidsjs.com/" rel="nofollow">FitVidsJS</a> &ndash; Chris Coyier and Paravel</li> <li><a href="https://github.com/i11ume/ghostHunter/" rel="nofollow">GhostHunter</a> &ndash; Jamal Neufeld</li> <li><a href="http://salvattore.com/" rel="nofollow">Salvattore</a> &ndash; Rolando Murillo and Giorgio Leveroni</li> <li><a href="http://mynameismatthieu.com/WOW/" rel="nofollow">WOWJS</a> &ndash; Matt Aussaguel, Webalys and Attila Ol&Atilde;&iexcl;h</li> <li><a href="https://github.com/mathiasbynens/jquery-placeholder" rel="nofollow">Placeholder.js</a> &ndash; Mathias Bynens</li> <h2 id="item-description__features">Features</h2> <li>Works with Ghost 0.5.10 &ndash; <strong>NEW</strong></li><li>You can add links from Ghost Dashboard &ndash; <strong>NEW</strong></li><li>Masonry Layout.</li> <li>Responsive.</li><li>Bootstrap 3.</li><li>Google Fonts.</li><li>Works with IE9+, Firefox, Chrome, Opera, Safari.</li> <li>Two color options: Dark and Light.</li> <li>Google Analytics.</li> <li>Disqus.</li> <li>Page Loader.</li> <li>Code Highlighting (+50 Languages).</li><li>12 Social Icons.</li> <li>Online Do