(599, 231, 'Thu Jan 22 14:52:43 +1100 2015', 'Tue Jan 27 06:45:53 +1100 2015', 'parichiti-a-tumblr-theme-for-portfolios', 'Parichiti - A Tumblr Theme for Portfolios', '\n    Present your artworks, graphic designs or illustrations, photographs or videos uniquely along two dimensions with this Tumblr theme for portfolios. Exploring your portfolio becomes intuitive and easy as both vertical and horizontal axes are used efficiently to arrange the items and their corresponding descriptions. Also, you continue to use your regular Tumblr dashboard to upload your works which are then neatly ordered in the frontend; no need to activate additional settings or upload your work elsewhere.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__logo">Logo</h3>\n\n    Add your logo for a consistent brand presence across the web.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__personalization-options">Personalization Options</h3>\n\n    Easily customize the colors, add social profiles and portfolio description for an optimized look and feel.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__showcase-your-work">Showcase Your Work</h3>\n\n    The clean and minimal interface of this theme places your work in the spotlight. Such is the layout that no more than one item at a time engages the attention of the viewer.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__device-agnostic">Device Agnostic</h3>\n\n    Be it touch screen or point and click, Parichiti retains its intuitive appeal and organization. Swiping omnidirectionally to explore your portfolio in mobile, tablet or touch enabled laptop and desktop devices remains a delightful experience.\n\n<h3 id="item-description__post-types-amp-pages">Post Types &amp; Pages</h3>\n\n    This theme, designed and developed for Tumblr based portfolios, supports all types of posts and pages.\n\n\n    <a href="http://thethemeshoppe-parichiti.tumblr.com/" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/MVJWqFo.png" alt="View live demo"></a>\n    <img src="http://i.imgur.com/c1oO4ri.png" alt="Don''t forget to rate">\n<h3 id="item-description__update-log">Update Log</h3>\n<pre>Parichiti v1.1 &acirc;&#128;&#148; CSS optimization\nParichiti v1.0 &acirc;&#128;&#148; Release</pre>', 'http://themeforest.net/theme_previews/9517967-parichiti-a-tumblr-theme-for-portfolios', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/120124420/themeforest-profile.__large_preview.jpg', 'http://themeforest.net/item/parichiti-a-tumblr-theme-for-portfolios/9517967', 'http://themeforest.net/item/parichiti-a-tumblr-theme-for-portfolios/full_screen_preview/9517967', 19, 'artists portfolio, creative, customizable design, gallery, graphic designer, minimalistic, photography, simple, touch friendly, tumblr portfolio, vertical & horizontal scroll', 1, 1, 1),
