(604, 212, 'Wed Mar 25 03:08:29 +1100 2015', 'Wed Mar 25 03:08:29 +1100 2015', 'premium-pricing-table', 'Premium Pricing Table', 'Premium Pricing Tables is a set of professionally designed pure CSS3 pricing tables that will give your product an outstanding sleek feel and look. The tables are built on a responsive 4 column grid which means they can fit in any design.\n\n\n	The package includes 2 dark and light CSS3 custom built style versions, 5 Smart color themes, extremely easy to style and customize, ability to highlight any columns as featured, CSS3 and JQuery animated, multiple theme color and all these features are consistent across all modern browsers including IE8+, smartphones and tablets.\n\n\n	Features:\n\n\n	3 Styles with 5 Smart Colors\nFull Responsive\nTwitter Bootstrap 3.3.2\nFont-awesome-4.3.0\nCSS3 Animation Effect\nJQuery Sliding Effect\nSimple &amp; Flexible\nFully Customizable\nEasy to Use', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10771408-premium-pricing-table', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127421130/preview.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/premium-pricing-table/10771408', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/premium-pricing-table/full_screen_preview/10771408', 4, '4 column pricing tables, css buttons, css pricing tables, css tooltips, css3 pricing tables, flexible grid, high resolution pricing tables, pricing, pricing tables, responsive, responsive pricing tables, smart pricing tables', 3, 3, 3),
(605, 213, 'Wed Mar 25 00:11:04 +1100 2015', 'Wed Mar 25 00:11:04 +1100 2015', 'the-one-radio-engine', 'The One Radio Engine', '<h3 id="item-description__summery">Summery</h3>\n  \nThe  One Radio Engine is like a CMS that&rsquo;s can be help you to create a online radio station website or Online radio shout casting. You can create or remove any page with any customized template that&rsquo;s are designed as this format. Tow type of admin access that can be more then secure to controlling admin panel. RJ profile, Scheduler, Image gallery, Slider image and user contact inbox also present here. Highly secured Radio Engine CMS, that created using CodeIgniter Framework.\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features</h3>\n  \n<li>Possible to set up Station IP or server</li>\n <li>Radio Shout casting</li>\n                    <li>Frontend Radio player.</li>\n                    <li>Admin can change site name, site email and site logo</li>\n                    <li>Possible to create customized page template</li>\n                    <li>Add or Remove page template</li>\n                    <li>Add or remove pages as you want</li>\n                    <li>CK editor integrated with page content</li>\n                    <li>More necessary template for frontend</li>\n                    <li>My profile page</li>\n                    <li>User contact message in admin panel</li>\n                    <li>Admin can reply to user contact via admin panel</li>\n                    <li>Email integrated with user contact and admin reply </li>\n                    <li>Admin can upload gallery image and also can deactivate for show.</li>\n                    <li>Frontend gallery image popup</li>\n                    <li>Admin can upload slider images and also can deactivate for show</li>\n                    <li>Admin can set &amp; delete RJ profile</li>\n                    <li>Admin can see the list of RJ profile</li>\n                    <li>RJ profile will be show in user frontend</li>