(606, 212, 'Thu Mar 26 02:16:06 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 26 02:16:06 +1100 2015', 'big-bold-css-button', 'Big Bold CSS Button', '<img src="http://brandsumo.com/images/screenshot-preview.jpg"><br><h2 id="item-description__big-bold-css-button">Big Bold CSS Button</h2>\n<br><strong>Big Bold CSS Button is a sharp, easy-to-use, configurable button set made in CSS3 for use in modern browsers. It is perfect for eye-catching download buttons or call-to-actions &ndash; and comes complete with an animated &lsquo;sheen&rsquo; effect on hover and smooth shadow effect on click.\n<br>\nIt includes an easy-to-use and simple <strong>Button Builder</strong> HTML document, with live updating Javascript button to demonstrate how the end result looks &ndash; Just select the parameters for your button and watch as it updates before your very eyes</strong>.\n<br>\nIt comes with 68 preset buttons, found in the buttons document, and uses Font Awesome icons by default &ndash; additional icon fonts can be added with basic knowledge of CSS &amp; HTML.\n<br><h2 id="item-description__features">Features</h2>\n<br><li><strong>Easy-to-use Button Builder</strong> to make it even easier to setup and configure buttons for use.</li>\n<li><strong>Instructional Document</strong> to explain functionality of the Button Builder.</li>\n<li><strong>34</strong> Rounded Preset Buttons and <strong>34</strong> Square Preset Buttons for a total of <strong>68</strong> Preset Bold CSS Buttons which are ready to use.</li>\n<li>Sheen animation when hovered.</li>\n<li>Shadow animation when clicked.</li>\n<li>Simple and understandable CSS code.</li>\n<br><img src="http://brandsumo.com/images/logo-envato.png">', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10880042-big-bold-css-button', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127282640/inline.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/big-bold-css-button/10880042', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/big-bold-css-button/full_screen_preview/10880042', 4, 'active, animated, button, buttons, color, css, css3