(608, 214, 'Wed Mar 25 08:00:20 +1100 2015', 'Thu Mar 26 01:07:26 +1100 2015', 'slidea-a-smarter-responsive-slider-plugin', 'Slidea - A Smarter Responsive Slider Plugin', '<img src="http://slideajs.com/assets/img/presentation.jpg" alt="Slidea by Pixobyte">\n\n\n	<img src="http://slideajs.com/assets/img/reviews/review2.jpg" alt="Slidea by Pixobyte"><img src="http://slideajs.com/assets/img/reviews/review1.jpg" alt="Slidea by Pixobyte">\n\n\n\n<strong>Slidea</strong> by Pixobyte is a super fast and intuitive multi-purpose content slider which completely leaves the competition behind. Slidea has been developed with simplicity, efficiency and innovation in mind, making it <strong>the perfect slider solution for your website</strong>. Built on the jQuery, VelocityJS and Animus animation framework, the slider was developed to offer the ultimate motion design experience.\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__features">Features</h3>\n\n                <h4 id="item-description__general">General</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Touch Enabled\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Layers and Objects\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Material Design Ready (by Google)\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Multiple Sliders\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Autoplay\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Pause on Hover\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Progress Bar\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Progress Bar Location\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Responsive Font\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Infinite Loop\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Custom Selectors\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Additional Classes\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__navigation">Navigation</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Controls\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Control Thumbnail\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Thumbnails\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Responsive Thumbnails\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Touch Enabled Thumbnails\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Mousewheel\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Scrolling Prevention\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Pagination\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Pagination Location\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__animation">Animation</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Fast VelocityJS Animations\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Animus Custom Animations\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        User Friendly Syntax (fade in, scale up)\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Object Animation Timeline\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Duration and Easing Control\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Unlimited Possibilities\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__layouts">Layouts</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Fluid Layout\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Responsive Layout\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Fullscreen Layout\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Content Layout\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        3D Carousel (Coming Soon)\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__videos">Videos</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Video Backgrounds\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Vimeo, YouTube and HTML5\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        API Play / Pause Functions\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Fully Responsive\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Pause Slider\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Volume Control\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Reset or Pause\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Autoplay\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__events">Events</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Custom Events API\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Slider Load Event\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Slide Change Event\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Pause Event\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Resume Event\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Resize Event\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__slidea-api">Slidea API</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Next Slide\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Previous Slide\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Go to nth Slide\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Pause Slider\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Resume Slider\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__developers">Developers</h4>\n                <li>\n                        Dynamic Caching\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        SCSS Theme Files\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Modular Plugin\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Visitor Design Pattern\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Layouter Class\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Easily Extendable\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        Great Documentation\n                    </li>\n                <h4 id="item-description__animations-differently">ANIMATIONS DIFFERENTLY</h4>\n\n\nWith Slidea you&rsquo;re never limited to animation presets. Each and every element of Slidea has states at certain moments of time. Because of the Animus Framework, all you need to do is to tell your slide in simple words to fade in, rotate z 45, scale up and it will animate accordingly.\n\n\n<h4 id="item-description__outstandingly-customizable">OUTSTANDINGLY CUSTOMIZABLE</h4>\n\n\nMake motion design happen directly in your website. Everything is possible with Slidea due to its intelligent API and modular nature, being suited for both beginners and experienced developers.\n\n\n<h4 id="item-description__extremely-efficient">EXTREMELY EFFICIENT</h4>\n\n\nInstead of excessive and unnecessary computing for every action, Slidea uses dynamic programming method to cache every detail in the memory. Compared to other slider plugins, Slidea is up to 3 times faster.\n\n\n<h4 id="item-description__so-many-features">SO MANY FEATURES</h4>\n\nSlidea offers many features which cannot be equalled by any other premium slider plugin. Created to be unique, efficient and intuitive, Slidea is a plugin made for everyone, from unexperienced users to fulltime developers.\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__updates">Updates</h3>\n\n	<strong>Version 1.1 2015/03/25</strong>\n<pre>\nAdded initial height to Slidea container to allow preloader to show\n-- assets/scss/slidea/themes/slidea.default.scss\n\nChanged js margin-top to css margin-top\n-- assets/js/theme/index.js\n-- assets/scss/theme/theme.scss\n</pre>\n\n\n	<strong>Version 1.0 2015/03/24</strong>\n<pre>\nInitial release\n</pre>', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10895461-slidea-a-smarter-responsive-slider-plugin', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127454313/preview.jpg', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/slidea-a-smarter-responsive-slider-plugin/10895461', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/slidea-a-smarter-responsive-slider-plugin/full_screen_preview/10895461', 14, '3d, animation, carousel, content, css3, grozav, html5, image, javascript, jquery, material design, pixobyte, plugin, slidea, slider', 0, 0, 0),
