(672, 213, 'Sat Mar 28 20:46:23 +1100 2015', 'Sat Mar 28 20:46:23 +1100 2015', 'vinnorokom-facebook-quiz-viral-app', 'Vinnorokom - Facebook Quiz viral app', '<h3 id="item-description__what-is-vinnorokom-facebook-quiz-viral-app">What is Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz viral app ?</h3>\nIt is a web based facebook viral quiz application. Due to the increasing number of \nfacebook user now a days,facebook is a great place of making fun and marketing as well. \nTo drive potential traffic from facebook, the quiz application runs a important role. Because of its conditional facebook share option, it goes viral.\n<br><a href="http://quiz.vinnorokom.com" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://vinnorokom.com/envato-image/Live-Preview.png"></a>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__see-demo-link">See Demo Link</h3>  \nWebsite : <a href="http://quiz.vinnorokom.com" rel="nofollow">http://quiz.vinnorokom.com</a><br>\nAdmin Demo : <a href="http://quiz.vinnorokom.com/admin-login" rel="nofollow">http://quiz.vinnorokom.com/admin-login</a><br>\nAdmin user : <a href="mailto:admin@admin.com">admin@admin.com</a><br>\nPass : 12345678<br><br><br><img src="http://vinnorokom.com/envato-image/Vinnorokom-banner_2_2_2_2.png" alt="Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz"><br><img src="http://vinnorokom.com/envato-image/Vinnorokom-banner.png" alt="Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz"><br><img src="http://vinnorokom.com/envato-image/Vinnorokom-banner_2.png" alt="Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz"><br><img src="http://vinnorokom.com/envato-image/Vinnorokom-banner_2_2.png" alt="Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz"><br><img src="http://vinnorokom.com/envato-image/Vinnorokom-banner_2_2_2.png" alt="Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz"><br><br><h3 id="item-description__admin-end-feature">Admin end feature</h3>\n\n\n	Easy installation process.<br>\n100% customizable code.<br>\nFully customizable real time preview homepage design.<br>\nSpammy user blocker/unblocker.<br>\nGoogle analytics and adsense setter.<br>\nUnlimited quiz creation.<br>\nPowerful Dashboard.<br>\nSimple Ajax page process .<br>\nScheduled quiz activation.<br>\nLead generation and viral marketing friendly.<br>\nViral facebook share system.<br>\nUser database as CSV download.<br><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__user-end-feature">User end feature</h3>\nQuiz play history . <br>\nQuiz progress count.<br>\nComplete result board.<br>More features coming soon in our next release.<br>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__compatibility">Compatibility</h3>\n\n	Responsive design for PC, Netbook,Phone,Tablet .<br>\nBrowser compatible with IE9+, Firefox, Opera, Chrome, Safari.<br> \nSupport <br>\nWe are very happy to support you any time 24/7. We appreciate your advice and suggestion for further development. \n<br><br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__quiz-updates">Quiz Updates :</h3>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__release-version-v-1-0-0">Release version &ndash;  V.1.0.0</h3>\n\n<h3 id="item-description__server-requirements">Server requirements:</h3>\nPHP &gt;= 5.3.7 <br>\nMCrypt PHP Extension<br>\n1 Mysql Database<br>\n30mb disk space<br><br><br><h3 id="item-description__technologies-and-libraries-used-in-vinnorokom-facebook-quiz">Technologies and libraries used in Vinnorokom Facebook Quiz </h3>\n\n	Laravel 4.0<br>\nBootstrap 3<br>\nAnimate css<br>\njQuery<br><br><br>\nAnd some laravel Packages<br>\niconfinder.com for using icons and free image<br>\n\n\n<h3 id="item-description__faq">FAQ:</h3>\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-i-have-no-idea-about-programming-may-still-install-run-and-customize-the"> Q: I have no idea about programming. May still install run and customize the app?</h3>\nAns : Yes. You do not need any programming knowledge . We have step by step installation manual in our documentation part. We need you only follow the documentation .If need any help please feel free to contact with us.\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-is-it-compatible-with-shared-or-dedicated-hosting"> Q: Is it compatible with shared or dedicated hosting?</h3>\nAns : Yes. Definitely it is compatible with any classical dedicated or shared hosting server.\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-can-i-restrict-one-user-or-spammer"> Q: Can i restrict one user or spammer ? </h3>\nAns: Simple! In the user option, there is a block button for every user. \nMenu? User? Action column? Block button\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-how-can-i-export-csv-for-all-users-information"> Q: How can I export csv for all users information ? </h3>\nAns : There is a Download CSV button on the top of user list.\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-is-there-any-limitation-for-playing-the-quiz"> Q: Is there any limitation for playing the quiz ? </h3>\nAns : No. It is unlimited.\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-how-many-group-can-i-create"> Q: How many group can i create? </h3>\nAns : You can create unlimited groups and Quizzes.\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-how-can-i-create-a-quiz-easily"> Q: How can i create a quiz easily? </h3>\nAns : Just follow the steps below: \nCreate a group? Write the quiz text? Select a group? Give options of the quiz? select the right answer.\nVideo tutorial: <a href="https://youtu.be/G13k0kF1k3M" rel="nofollow">https://youtu.be/G13k0kF1k3M</a>\n<h3 id="item-description__-q-how-can-i-perform-scheduled-quiz"> Q: How can i perform scheduled quiz? </h3>\nAns : Just go to the option Quiz setting? select the group? Select the time duration From&acirc;&#128;&#148;To.', 'http://codecanyon.net/theme_previews/10869572-vinnorokom-facebook-quiz-viral-app', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/127872912/banner590x300.png', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/vinnorokom-facebook-quiz-viral-app/10869572', 'http://codecanyon.net/item/vinnorokom-facebook-quiz-viral-app/full_screen_preview/10869572', 14, 'brand marketing, facebook app, Facebook lead generation, facebook quiz, facebook viral marketing, Facebook viral quiz, Lead generation app, Marketing with fun, Mobile quiz, online quiz, Vinnorokom, Vinnrokom app store, viral app, viral quiz, Viral qu', 0, 0, 0),
