(699, 218, 'Sat Nov 16 06:27:21 +1100 2013', 'Sat Nov 16 06:27:21 +1100 2013', 'z-runner-endless-game-starter-kit-for-unity3d', 'Z-Runner Endless Game Starter Kit for Unity3D', '<a href="http://activeden.net/item/zrunner-endless-game-starter-kit-for-unity3d/6136014/support#">Frequently Asked Questions</a>\n<br><h2 id="item-description__webplayer-demo">WebPlayer Demo:</h2>\n<a href="http://kiavash2k.com/assets/products/zrunner/" rel="nofollow">\n<img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/zrunnerdemoplay.jpg"></a>\n<br><br><h2 id="item-description__updates">Updates: </h2>\none of my buyers don&rsquo;t like the way I play the Z sounds and I do an update for you all. please use this too when you purchase the item, if you wish to play the Z sound when the Zombies is near you. (Maybe The better way)<br><br>\nfor using this update please overwrite this cs file into your project.\nUpdate v0.1: <a href="http://www.kiavash2k.com/products/updates/zrunner/ZombieAudioManager.cs" rel="nofollow">ZombieAudioManager.cs</a>, I am available for more customizations.\n<br><br><h2 id="item-description__gameplay">Gameplay:</h2>\nYou are a man running on the jungle and you need to avoid the Z(Zombies), move left or right to avoid Z(s) and the Jungle Trees.<br><br><h2 id="item-description__features">Features:</h2>\n<li>This package contain full <strong>Unity3D Project Files</strong> and <strong>Sourcecode in C#</strong>\n</li>\n<li>\nWe have a <strong>class</strong> to generate the <strong>platforms (ground)</strong> this component allow you to easily change the ground mesh without any coding, you just need to change the <strong>prefabs</strong> for changing the grounds, it called Infinite Terrain.<br><br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/infinite-Terrain.jpg"><br></li>\n<li>\nFor changing or editing the game models no programming is required and you can change anything easily.\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Jump</strong> feature is also available in game core.\n</li>\n<li>\nYou can change the number of zombies, trees or other generated items.\n</li>\n<li>\nThe generator use <strong>UNIQUE</strong> name for <strong>spawning items</strong> so you can use two or more same components for generatig the zombies or trees at the same time.<br><br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/zombie-spawn.jpg"><br></li>\n<li>\nThe game is <strong>endless</strong> or <strong>infinite</strong> \n</li>\n<li>\nThe new idea for generating scene <strong>FOG</strong> for mobile system this can cost less <strong>Memory</strong> and <strong>CPU</strong>.\n</li>\n<li>\nEasy to add other <strong>Creatures</strong> than Z for gameplay.\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Highscore</strong> system is also available\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Mainmenu</strong>, <strong>Gameover</strong> and <strong>HUD</strong> codes are also available.\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Auto Screen Orientation</strong> feature is also worked fine\n</li>\n<li>\nThe Game has <strong>sound</strong> too and you can customize the sounds very well\n</li>\n<h2 id="item-description__game-play-and-controls">Game Play and Controls:</h2>\nFor playing the game <strong>tap the screen</strong> to start play. <br><br>\nin game mode when you <strong>tap of the half left side</strong> of the screen you go left and if you <strong>tap on the right half</strong> you go right, the is about avoiding the <strong>Z(s)</strong> and escape more <strong>distance</strong>, the game also has the <strong>jump state</strong> in <strong>core</strong> but never be used in this game play. you can implement your ideas with this too.<br><br><strong>Hope You Enjoy!</strong>', 'http://activeden.net/theme_previews/6136014-zrunner-endless-game-starter-kit-for-unity3d', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/72889976/BigMain.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/zrunner-endless-game-starter-kit-for-unity3d/6136014', '', 27, 'android, dead, device, game kit, gamekit, mobile, run, runner, starter, unity3d, z, zombie, zombie run, zrunner', 0, 0, 0),
(700, 218, 'Thu Oct 17 04:27:03 +1100 2013', 'Thu Oct 17 04:27:03 +1100 2013', '3rd-person-camera-script', '3rd Person Camera Script', 'Script implements camera zoom, horizontal and vertical orbital camera movements; check camera collisions and change camera position.\nEverything you need is to add this script to the Main Camera.\n\n\n	Use mouse scroll to zoom in/out. \nUse right mouse button for orbital rotations.\n\n\n	Script has parameters for Camera setup: Camera angle, zoom speed, min and max zoom, vertical and horizontal mouse speed, vertical tilt limits, dumping speed.\n\n\n	Package contains Standard Unity Assets (3rd Person Controller and Skybox) just for demonstration.\n\n\n	The script is written in C# and commented. There is a description file in the project, where you can see explanations about script.', 'http://activeden.net/theme_previews/5494486-3rd-person-camera-script', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/65408553/3rdcamera_preview_590x300.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/3rd-person-camera-script/5494486', '', 5, '3rd, c-sharp, camera, collide, collision, controller, game, orbit, package, person, scene, script, unity, unity3d, zoom', 0, 0, 0),
(701, 218, 'Thu Oct 17 05:40:49 +1100 2013', 'Thu Oct 17 05:40:49 +1100 2013', 'object-rotation-script', 'Object Rotation Script', 'ObjectRotation Script.\n\n\n	Script implements 3d rotations with different speed and directions. Also possible to set random rotation. Just add this script to your object(s) and set parameters.\n\n\n	Script has input parameters(see image preview and webplayer):\nRotateX &ndash; enable/disable x rotation\nRotateY &ndash; enable/disable y rotation\nRotateZ &ndash; enable/disable z rotation\nClockwiseX &ndash; set clockwise or counterclockwise direction\nClockwiseY &ndash; set clockwise or counterclockwise direction\nClockwiseZ &ndash; set clockwise or counterclockwise direction\nRotationSpeedX &ndash; set x-axis rotation speed\nRotationSpeedX &ndash; set y-axis rotation speed\nRotationSpeedX &ndash; set z-axis rotation speed\nRandomRotation &ndash; enable/disable random rotation\nTime &ndash; time for changing random rotation\n\n\n	Package contains demonstration scene.\n\n\n	The script is written in C# and commented.', 'http://activeden.net/theme_previews/5655614-object-rotation-script', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/67368202/objectrotations_preview590x300.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/object-rotation-script/5655614', '', 5, 'c-sharp, clockwise, counterclockwise, direction, game, object, package, rotation, scene, script, unity, unity3d', 1, 1, 1),
(702, 218, 'Tue Oct 22 08:24:29 +1100 2013', 'Tue Oct 22 08:24:29 +1100 2013', 'tomahawk', 'Tomahawk', '<strong>Hack &amp; slay your way through Hordes of Monsters with this Tomahawk!</strong>\n\n\n<strong>Features</strong>\n	<li>Ships with Diffuse-, Normal- and Specular Map</li>\n		<li>LowPoly and therefore mobile-friendly</li>\n		<li>UV-Layout included, so you can design the Tomahawk as you like</li>\n	', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/68167380/preview-image.png', 'http://activeden.net/item/tomahawk/5722361', '', 3, 'lowpoly, tomahawk', 2, 2, 2),
(703, 218, 'Thu Oct 17 04:23:10 +1100 2013', 'Thu Oct 17 04:23:10 +1100 2013', 'angry-footballs', 'Angry Footballs', 'MEET ANGRY FOOTBALLS. This is funny parody to one famous game about birds with strange suicidal behaviour. \nIn year 2050 only robots plays serious football championships. They kick footballs every day very hard and restless.\nSo footballs get really angry and they will revenge on those who kick them!!!\nHelp Angry Footbals to revenge and punish robots.\n<br>\nAngry Footballs is an android game running successful on play store\n<br><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ap.angryfootballs" rel="nofollow">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ap.angryfootballs</a>', 'http://activeden.net/theme_previews/5489357-angry-footballs', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/65348992/Cover.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/angry-footballs/5489357', '', 27, '2d, android, angry, footballs, mobile, physics, raycast, robots, slingshot, strategic', 1, 1, 1),
(704, 218, 'Thu Oct 17 05:27:47 +1100 2013', 'Thu Oct 17 05:27:47 +1100 2013', 'military-helicopter-with-fly-and-firing-mechanism', 'Military Helicopter with Fly and Firing Mechanism', '<h2 id="item-description__click-to-play-the-demo"><strong><a href="http://www.logical-brains.com/projects/niraj/military-helicopter-with-fly-and-firing-mechanism/" rel="nofollow">Click To Play The Demo</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n<h2 id="item-description__military-helicopter-with-fly-and-firing-mechanism"><strong>Military Helicopter with Fly and Firing Mechanism</strong></h2>\n\n\n	<strong>Description:</strong> This Unity Project is about the sophisticated military helicopter control mechanism along with firing system. This Project consists of the following attributes:\n\n\n<li>Military Helicopter or Chopper.</li>\n<li>Chopper or Helicopter can fly up, down, rotate at single position, rotate with movement and can fire with following controls:\n\n<ol><li>W &ndash; Fly Upward/Take Off</li>\n<li>S  &ndash; Fly Downward/Take Down</li>\n<li>A &ndash; Fly Through Left Alignment</li>\n<li>D &ndash; Fly through Right Alignment</li>\n\n<li>UP Arrow &ndash; Move Backward</li>\n<li>Down Arrow &ndash; Move Forward</li>\n<li>Left Arrow &ndash; Rotate Left</li>\n<li>Right Arrow &ndash; Rotate Right</li>\n\n<li>Fire &ndash; Left Mouse Button</li>\n</ol></li>\n<li>When bullets strike any physical object in front of strike line it will create an impact of bullet strike effect at the impact position.</li>\n<li>Helicopter/Chopper fires bullets with the machine gun sound so that it looks real.</li>\n\nAll the above Attributes, Functioning and Assets can be edited according your need.\n\n	Please mail me for any kind of Help or Support at <a href="mailto:Nirajv21@gmail.com">Nirajv21@gmail.com</a>.  I will be Happy to Help You. <img src="/images/smileys/happy.png" alt=":)" title=":)">', 'http://activeden.net/theme_previews/5651163-military-helicopter-with-fly-and-firing-mechanism', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/67313197/Preview%20Image.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/military-helicopter-with-fly-and-firing-mechanism/5651163', '', 27, 'chopper fly mechanism, helicopter fly, military chopper control, military chopper firing, military chopper unity 3d 4, military helicopter contro, military helicopter firing, military helicopter fly, military helicopter unity 3d, unity 3d helicopter ', 0, 0, 0),
(705, 218, 'Wed Oct 30 09:35:34 +1100 2013', 'Wed Oct 30 09:35:34 +1100 2013', 'highway-racing-mobile', 'Highway Racing Mobile', '<a href="http://activeden.net/item/highway-racing-mobile/5988824/support">Frequently Asked Questions</a>\n<br><br>\nwell commented Unity Project is included in this package, The Starter Game-Kit is tested on <strong>Samsung Galaxy Tab 8.0, LG &ndash; NEXUS 4</strong>, <strong>LG &ndash; E400</strong> and <strong>SONY XPERIA U</strong>, There is no lag at all on play and the game run smooth, completely optimized for devices.\n<br><br>\nTested on Android Devices:<br>\n- SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab 8.0<br>\n- LG Nexus 4<br>\n- LG E-400 [Android 2.3.6]<br> \n- Sony XPERIA U<br><br><br>\nThe game automatically remove the generated platforms to reduce the System Resources usage (such as memory, storage, GPU and CPU), so the game is wonderfully optimized and running fast and smooth on devices. (BUY and learn about the idea behind the game and how it will manage memory, for running faster on devices)\n<br><br>\nScreenplay on Devices:\n<br>\nSamsung Galaxy Tab 7.0:<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/galaxy.jpg"><br>\nLG Nexus 4:<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/LGNexus4.jpg"><br>\nLG E-400:<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/lge400.jpg"><br><br>\nThis game is designed to <strong>simply customized</strong> by your <strong>ideas</strong>.\n<br><br><strong>New Features:</strong><br>\n- You can use 2 or more Gem Generator to spawn more gems. <br>\n- You can add 2 or more Car Generator for more terrafic. <br>\n- You can add 2 or more Jump Generator for more jump pads.<br><br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/highwayMobile/car2.jpg"><br><br>\n- All of the meshes can be replaced easily in just one drag and drop you just need to add/Remove from each component array.<br><br>\n- Jump Pads:<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/highwayMobile/carjump.jpg"><br>\n- Gem Generator:<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/highwayMobile/Gem.jpg"><br>\n- Map Maker: you can easily customize from road to jungle or etc.<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/highwayMobile/road.jpg"><br>\n-Each collectable item can have individual catch SCORE and catch sound and the cars can have random body color or not.<br><img src="http://www.kiavash2k.com/FBPage/highwayMobile/entity.jpg"><br><br>\n... and more features are available.\n<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>\n- Road Generator (fully customizable)<br>\n- Gem Generator (fully customizable)<br>\n- Car / AI / Block Generator  (fully customizable)<br>\n- Jump Pad Generator (fully customizable)<br>\n- Pause <br>\n- Menu <br>\n- GameOver <br>\n- Coin Genrator (fully customizable) simple to change score of each gem or coin<br>\n- Explode Particle and screen effect  (fully customizable)<br>\n- Scene Music<br>\n- Coin Catch Custom SFX<br>\n- and many more feature.<br><br>\n- The scripts are in c# and well commented so you can easily modify the game features.<br><br>', 'http://activeden.net/theme_previews/5988824-highway-racing-mobile', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/71342152/BigMain.jpg', 'http://activeden.net/item/highway-racing-mobile/5988824', '', 27, 'android, car, coin, endless, game, highway, infinite, ios, mobile, race, racing, road, run, score, unity', 1, 1, 1),
(706, 218, 'Tue Oct 22 09:18:44 +1100 2013', 'Tue Oct 22 09:18:44 +1100 2013', 'fish-school-bass', 'Fish School: Bass', 'Features\n\n\n	Scripted Fish School perfect for underwater scenes. This asset is very simple to use, simply drag the prefab to the stage. Commented inspector editor will assist in achieving the desired result.\n<br><br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Drag &amp; Drop Fish School<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Gizmos that shows roaming area<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Simple UV map, easy to change texture<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Easily customize amount, size and speed<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Animation speed based on fish movement<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; 354 tris animated model<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; 2048&times;2048px max texture resolution<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Easy to add custom animated models<br>\n&acirc;&#128;&cent; Includes Bubbles and Demo Scene<br><br><br><a href="http://chemicalbliss.com/portfolio/unity/fishSchoolBass/WebPlayer/fullscreen.html" rel="nofollow"><strong> &gt; WebPlayer Demo </strong></a>', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/68709728/preview.png', 'http://activeden.net/item/fish-school-bass/5756201', '', 16, 'animated, bass, fish, fish school, school', 2, 2, 2),
(707, 218, 'Thu Oct 17 04:13:59 +1100 2013', 'Thu Oct 17 04:13:59 +1100 2013', 'jet-plane-starter-kit', 'Jet Plane Starter Kit', '100% Physics plane.\n<br>\nIt&rsquo;s so easy to create new map, just create new scene, then drag and drop the &ldquo;Aircraft&rdquo; prefab, and you are ready for takeoff!\n<br><br>\nCONTROLS:\n<br>\nARROW UP -Pitch fwd\n<br>\nARROW DOWN &ndash; Pitch down\n<br>\nARROW LEFT &ndash; Roll left\n<br>\nARROW RIGHT &ndash; Roll right\n<br>\nW &ndash; Accelerate \n<br>\nS &ndash; Decelerate \n<br>\nA &ndash; Steer right\n<br>\nD &ndash; Steer left\n<br>\nLEFT SHIFT &ndash; Shoot\n<br>\n//Don&rsquo;t forget to hold &ldquo;S&rdquo; button when landing.\n<br><a href="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/78819580/oldproject/Desktop.html" rel="nofollow">WEB PLAYER</a>', '', 'https://0.s3.envato.com/files/64868081/Preview.png', 'http://activeden.net/item/jet-plane-starter-kit/5447451', '', 27, 'aircraft, jet, physics, plane', 2, 2, 2),
